WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:47.079
My lord...

3
00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:50.599
My lord...

4
00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:57.639
My lord...

5
00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:00.279
My lord...

6
00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:42.319
Stop. woman!

7
00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:48.399
Where is your path?

8
00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:50.279
To Kizl Elma!

9
00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:55.039
How happy are the mothers of those
who sharpen their swords on that path!

10
00:02:56.040 --> 00:03:00.199
To their sons and daughters
they breastfed at dawn...

11
00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:04.519
blood with the milk they
breastfed. glory with lullabies...

12
00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:09.719
To the Turkish woman who raised children by
giving them faith with the love of Allah.

13
00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:14.439
Threes. sevens. forties...

14
00:03:14.440 --> 00:03:16.439
to the time and
era of true men...

15
00:03:18.160 --> 00:03:22.239
for the love of Hak Teala.
who honored us with faith.

16
00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:23.399
Thank you.

17
00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.799
In which direction
is Kizil Elma?

18
00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:28.879
Please tell.

19
00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:11.959
Peace be upon you.

20
00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:13.719
And upon you be peace.

21
00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:15.559
And upon you be peace.

22
00:04:18.200 --> 00:04:20.879
Kayil's woman. the
true mother of Turks.

23
00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:22.679
Please tell.

24
00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:32.999
Noble woman who awaits
her husband's return...

25
00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:36.719
We wanted to hear about
Kayi's situation from you as well.

26
00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:42.239
But we asked you to tell us what a
mother's eyes see. what she hears...

27
00:04:42.760 --> 00:04:47.999
what she sees. what she hears.
what we don't see. what we don't hear.

28
00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:52.159
Ertugrul and Osman Bey took
many towns from the infidels...

29
00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:55.639
and established a new homeland.

30
00:04:56.480 --> 00:05:01.039
But will this homeland
turn into a powerful state...

31
00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:03.039
if Osman Bey meets his Lord?

32
00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:07.839
You are worried that Osman
Bey's life might not be long enough.

33
00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:09.359
I understand.

34
00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:12.639
Wouldn't you. Malhun Hatun?

35
00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:14.559
Who is your concern for?

36
00:05:17.040 --> 00:05:17.679
It's for Orhan.

37
00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:23.119
We heard that you
are backing Orhan.

38
00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:29.039
Don't you know that changing the course
of a river causes all sorts of disasters?

39
00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:29.559
Don't you know?

40
00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:36.999
Why Orhan? Do you show weakness
because he is your own child?

41
00:05:40.280 --> 00:05:43.999
There is no distinction between my
children. whether they are my own or not.

42
00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:48.919
We have been kneaded with the same
yeast and become one for forty years.

43
00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:52.879
Osman Bey has
given Alaeddin a duty.

44
00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:54.679
Orhan will not accept it.

45
00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:58.479
Alaeddin does
not know tradition.

46
00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:02.559
You are devoid of bravery.
that's why you favor Orhan.

47
00:06:06.040 --> 00:06:10.199
So much so that you succumb to maternal
weaknesses and cannot see the truth.

48
00:06:10.200 --> 00:06:11.439
Do you think I am blind?

49
00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:17.239
On the contrary. I
think like Osman Bey.

50
00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:21.439
The pelt belongs to
whoever deserves it.

51
00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:31.959
However. whoever takes Bursa will not be content
with the pelt. he will ascend to the throne.

52
00:06:31.960 --> 00:06:35.359
He will not be content with a
beylik. he will become a sultan.

53
00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:41.039
And that candidate. until
proven otherwise. in my eyes...

54
00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:45.359
is Orhan Bey.

55
00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:56.519
Orhan!

56
00:06:56.760 --> 00:06:57.119
Where is he?

57
00:06:57.520 --> 00:06:57.799
Father!

58
00:06:58.600 --> 00:06:59.239
Where is Alaeddin?

59
00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:01.399
Rast went to call
him. what happened?

60
00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:02.799
My Osman!

61
00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:09.799
To see you like this. I wish I had
died in the dungeons of Bursa. right?

62
00:07:10.520 --> 00:07:11.119
My father!

63
00:07:12.280 --> 00:07:12.639
Father!

64
00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:14.839
What's wrong with my father?

65
00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:16.639
Your father will be
fine. my daughter.

66
00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:17.119
Brother!

67
00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:20.479
What if something
happens to my father?

68
00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:22.039
He will be fine.

69
00:07:25.640 --> 00:07:26.919
He is Osman Bey.

70
00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:31.639
Osman?

71
00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:33.919
Osman!

72
00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.079
Osman!

73
00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:38.679
We are here. my father.

74
00:07:41.520 --> 00:07:41.919
My Bey!

75
00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:43.879
Don't worry. we are all here.

76
00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:47.079
Thanks be to Allah.

77
00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:57.999
In your absence.
everyone knows their duty.

78
00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:01.439
Osman!

79
00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:03.999
Osman. what
kind of talk is that?

80
00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:05.119
Osman!

81
00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:12.399
Only Allah knows what
will happen. woman.

82
00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:29.399
Your duty is to protect the
unity and order of the oba.

83
00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:32.759
My Bey!

84
00:08:32.760 --> 00:08:33.399
Father!

85
00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:37.119
Osman!

86
00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:39.159
My Bey!

87
00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:42.919
My Bey. open your
eyes. open them. my Bey!

88
00:08:43.400 --> 00:08:43.799
Father!

89
00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:49.239
Where is that?

90
00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:53.919
Unity in the oba means order.
it means my father. mother.

91
00:08:54.640 --> 00:08:55.999
He goes to fulfill his duty.

92
00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.959
I will get the cure from
the one who gave the pain.

93
00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.519
Brother. what will happen here?

94
00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.959
The infidel's poison is
circulating throughout his body.

95
00:09:06.280 --> 00:09:07.159
Poison? What poison?

96
00:09:07.160 --> 00:09:10.519
This word "poison” will
not leave this tent. Alaaddin.

97
00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:14.719
We will not let them say that they couldn't protect our
Osman Bey in his own tent and thus embolden the enemy.

98
00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:15.159
We will not encourage.

99
00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:17.039
My father is entrusted to you.

100
00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:18.359
Where are you going?

101
00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:21.759
Either you will find
that cure or I will bring it.

102
00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:24.839
Until it's found. sleep is
forbidden for both you and me.

103
00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:26.319
He's entrusted to you.

104
00:09:26.360 --> 00:09:26.799
Thanks.

105
00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:35.879
Bring me that physician. Kara.

106
00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.399
The candle has just gone out.

107
00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:47.999
He left a short while ago.

108
00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:49.479
He's escaping.

109
00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:49.799
It's obvious.

110
00:09:56.840 --> 00:10:00.839
Halime Hatun. the physician just left from
behind the tribe with his bag and horse.

111
00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:03.759
He realized he would be
caught. of course. the scoundrel.

112
00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:05.039
Inform my brother.

113
00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:06.679
Esma. prepare the
horses immediately.

114
00:10:07.160 --> 00:10:07.439
Come on.

115
00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:13.879
Is there permission. my Bey?

116
00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:14.919
Come. Ali. come.

117
00:10:18.520 --> 00:10:20.879
My Bey. the
physician has escaped.

118
00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.199
It's not that easy.

119
00:10:26.800 --> 00:10:27.959
You stay here. Kara Halil.

120
00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:29.519
Leaving the tribe
empty is not an option.

121
00:10:30.520 --> 00:10:30.879
Come on.

122
00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.919
Is there permission. my Bey?

123
00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:26.959
Come. my son. come.

124
00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:34.639
Osman Bey. father. Alaaddin Bey
doesn't want it to be heard in the tribe.

125
00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:36.919
but the situation is bad.

126
00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:42.519
Osman Bey.

127
00:11:48.760 --> 00:11:51.639
Now is not the time for
mourning. but for prudence.

128
00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:58.519
My Osman Bey. Fatma Hatun was
supposed to bring ammunition from Inegol.

129
00:11:58.720 --> 00:11:59.399
For the encampment.

130
00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:01.199
You will meet her.

131
00:12:05.880 --> 00:12:07.439
You will show yourself well.

132
00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:10.279
Here. my honorable father.

133
00:12:12.960 --> 00:12:14.479
Alright then.

134
00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:19.519
My son. my brave
one. look. did you see?

135
00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:22.119
There is good in
every evil. my child.

136
00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:26.599
This duty is an opportunity
for you to win Fatma's heart.

137
00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:29.359
The poor girl is very fond
of her father. you know.

138
00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:31.839
Go be with her. comfort her.

139
00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:33.159
She is not like Halime.

140
00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:34.919
Don't leave her alone.

141
00:12:35.280 --> 00:12:35.799
Right. my son?

142
00:12:36.280 --> 00:12:37.239
Don't worry. mother.

143
00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:38.239
Alright.

144
00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:39.439
Come on then.

145
00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:22.079
This is not a decanter.

146
00:13:23.440 --> 00:13:24.439
It clearly has visitors.

147
00:14:13.200 --> 00:14:14.439
What are you doing here?

148
00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:19.039
Didn't I tell you not to come unless
you had to. unless the poison ran out?

149
00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:20.879
Osman Bey's
condition is very bad.

150
00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:22.359
I fear he will die.

151
00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:24.279
You couldn't manage one task.

152
00:14:25.040 --> 00:14:25.719
Return to the tribe immediately.

153
00:14:26.160 --> 00:14:28.119
If Osman dies. you will die too.

154
00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:28.959
I can't return.

155
00:14:30.280 --> 00:14:31.639
They will suspect me then.

156
00:14:33.520 --> 00:14:34.399
But...

157
00:14:34.400 --> 00:14:36.279
I have important news.

158
00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:40.399
A caravan will come
to the tribe from Inegol.

159
00:14:41.040 --> 00:14:41.999
It's full of ammunition.

160
00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:45.839
And Osman Bey's daughter.
Fatma. is leading the caravan.

161
00:14:46.400 --> 00:14:46.879
My sister!

162
00:14:51.040 --> 00:14:52.439
I also sent word to Guvercin.

163
00:14:52.920 --> 00:14:54.199
Thanks to me.
everyone will know.

164
00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:55.919
Then we don't need you anymore.

165
00:14:56.560 --> 00:14:56.959
Kill him.

166
00:14:57.720 --> 00:14:58.119
Halime!

167
00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:51.799
Tell me.

168
00:15:54.280 --> 00:15:55.959
They told me to
poison Osman Bey.

169
00:15:56.520 --> 00:15:57.199
To make him very ill.

170
00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:01.359
But not to kill him.

171
00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:02.999
They said he should remain sick.

172
00:16:04.040 --> 00:16:04.319
Him.

173
00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:06.439
Not his death...

174
00:16:06.440 --> 00:16:07.639
his illness is what
we need. they said.

175
00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:10.599
I didn't know it would
turn out like this.

176
00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:12.519
Gunyesi couldn't take it.

177
00:16:13.040 --> 00:16:14.719
My lord. please don't kill me.

178
00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:17.319
Who told you to
poison my father?

179
00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.039
How did you poison him?

180
00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:19.599
It's all here.

181
00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:21.559
Allow me.

182
00:16:56.760 --> 00:16:58.799
The physician's
dagger was poisoned.

183
00:17:07.720 --> 00:17:08.719
Well done. physician.

184
00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:11.959
He applied poison to his
foot instead of ointment.

185
00:17:12.600 --> 00:17:14.719
The infidel has
entered the tent.

186
00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.399
Orhan Bey is right.

187
00:17:19.120 --> 00:17:21.479
We shouldn't even tell the
beys about this poison matter.

188
00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:24.079
They put us in a
difficult situation.

189
00:17:25.320 --> 00:17:27.799
My lord appointed you
as regent just in time.

190
00:17:28.040 --> 00:17:28.639
I explained. my lord.

191
00:17:29.120 --> 00:17:31.239
I did not allow the oba
to be left without a leader.

192
00:17:31.240 --> 00:17:35.079
Before the infidels take advantage
of my Osman Bey's illness...

193
00:17:35.080 --> 00:17:37.079
it is time to attack
the enemy quickly.

194
00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:41.119
Let them see that if my
Osman Bey is not here...

195
00:17:41.120 --> 00:17:42.439
my Alahattin Bey is.

196
00:17:43.880 --> 00:17:45.959
What's the rush. Sahinsah Bey?

197
00:17:46.920 --> 00:17:48.839
My Osman Bey is
alive. thank goodness.

198
00:17:50.080 --> 00:17:53.319
It is all of our wish for him to
live even longer. Malhun Hatun.

199
00:17:54.320 --> 00:17:56.399
It is for him to be at our
head for many more years.

200
00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:58.559
My Osman Bey's wish is...

201
00:17:58.560 --> 00:18:00.479
my Alaattin Bey's regency.

202
00:18:01.480 --> 00:18:03.239
Both in his life
and in his death.

203
00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:05.479
He made him regent in his life.

204
00:18:06.400 --> 00:18:08.159
He won't be regent in his
death. it will be a transfer.

205
00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:13.319
Thank God. that
time has not come yet.

206
00:18:15.360 --> 00:18:16.199
Mother...

207
00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:20.239
we haven't even come to the
time to say these words yet. mother.

208
00:18:21.040 --> 00:18:22.319
You should tell
this not to me...

209
00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:25.679
but to the one who
brought this up. Alaattin.

210
00:18:27.160 --> 00:18:29.359
Just think about what has
happened in recent days.

211
00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:32.439
Is someone's ambition
to put you on the throne...

212
00:18:32.440 --> 00:18:34.919
or to follow your
brother's lead?

213
00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:40.999
Malhun Hatun...

214
00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:44.119
you should show your love for
your son by supporting Alaattin.

215
00:18:45.320 --> 00:18:47.159
Not by putting
doubts in his mind.

216
00:18:48.120 --> 00:18:51.119
Do your ears hear what comes
out of your mouth. Sahinsah Bey?

217
00:18:51.760 --> 00:18:54.199
I would not forgive anyone who
dares to question my love for my child...

218
00:18:54.520 --> 00:18:57.679
even if he were my Bey's
brother. not just his companion.

219
00:18:58.640 --> 00:18:59.159
Mother...

220
00:18:59.640 --> 00:19:00.519
enough. mother.

221
00:19:01.760 --> 00:19:02.599
Enough.

222
00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:09.039
Sahinsah Bey. you must
inform the beys immediately.

223
00:19:10.160 --> 00:19:11.279
A council will be
convened at once.

224
00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:18.399
There is no time to spend
on a council. Alaattin Bey.

225
00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:20.639
And there is no need.
the seal is with you.

226
00:19:21.280 --> 00:19:22.199
Your word is a command.

227
00:19:23.320 --> 00:19:25.159
You speak truly. Sahingsah
Bey. you speak truly.

228
00:19:25.800 --> 00:19:26.519
The command is mine.

229
00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:30.479
My command is
a council. at once.

230
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:35.559
The right thing to do
is to wait for Orhan Bey.

231
00:19:36.040 --> 00:19:37.039
Mother...

232
00:19:37.040 --> 00:19:39.999
the state no longer has
time to wait for Orhan.

233
00:19:41.040 --> 00:19:41.879
Mother...

234
00:19:46.520 --> 00:19:48.399
They are going to raid my
sister's incoming caravan. brother.

235
00:19:48.800 --> 00:19:50.999
We know. we will
take our precautions.

236
00:19:52.640 --> 00:19:53.359
Don't say anything to my mother.

237
00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:58.199
No. there is nothing here
about the antidote for the poison.

238
00:19:59.880 --> 00:20:02.039
My father's cure is within
the reach of this pigeon.

239
00:20:02.800 --> 00:20:04.119
Those who raided
Fatma's caravan...

240
00:20:04.480 --> 00:20:07.079
will lead us to those who
did this evil to my father.

241
00:20:08.360 --> 00:20:10.319
Only this way can we
find my father's cure.

242
00:20:14.200 --> 00:20:15.199
The game they
are playing is big.

243
00:20:16.280 --> 00:20:17.639
They want to create
division in the oba.

244
00:20:18.320 --> 00:20:19.879
There is no division
in Kay| Oba. brother.

245
00:20:20.520 --> 00:20:21.399
My naive brother.

246
00:20:22.560 --> 00:20:24.159
Wherever there are
humans. there is duality.

247
00:20:25.040 --> 00:20:26.199
Especially if there's
power involved...

248
00:20:27.560 --> 00:20:30.839
and power is won not by those
who fight. but by those who deserve it.

249
00:20:32.320 --> 00:20:34.719
Go to my sister.
tell them to prepare.

250
00:20:35.960 --> 00:20:37.199
Let's return to the tent.

251
00:20:38.120 --> 00:20:39.639
I will tell Alaaddin everything.

252
00:20:40.760 --> 00:20:42.199
Either I will break
this dirty game...

253
00:20:43.400 --> 00:20:45.439
or this game will
break our unity.

254
00:20:46.160 --> 00:20:48.439
Come on. walk.

255
00:20:52.320 --> 00:20:55.439
Malhun Hatun. my Bey's
condition is not good at all.

256
00:20:56.320 --> 00:20:59.039
What? Father. father!

257
00:21:17.560 --> 00:21:17.919
My brother!

258
00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:24.879
My brother!

259
00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:29.999
I'm fine.

260
00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:36.759
Boran Bey. get well soon.

261
00:21:37.600 --> 00:21:38.239
I hope you are well.

262
00:21:39.120 --> 00:21:40.399
Alhamdulillah. my brother.

263
00:21:41.600 --> 00:21:42.159
My brother.

264
00:21:46.520 --> 00:21:47.799
Get well soon. Boran Bey.

265
00:21:48.880 --> 00:21:50.399
Thank you. thank you.

266
00:21:50.640 --> 00:21:51.319
Get well soon.

267
00:21:52.400 --> 00:21:53.519
Let me check again.

268
00:21:55.160 --> 00:21:55.999
You're fine.

269
00:21:58.320 --> 00:21:59.359
You have wounds.

270
00:22:00.360 --> 00:22:01.719
But what can they do to you?

271
00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:02.559
Get well soon.

272
00:22:03.880 --> 00:22:05.079
My lion brother.

273
00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:11.199
Do your spears wound mountains?

274
00:22:12.600 --> 00:22:14.519
You have ruined Flavius's game.

275
00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:16.559
We will do more to him.

276
00:22:19.960 --> 00:22:21.759
May your holy war
be blessed. sirs.

277
00:22:22.080 --> 00:22:25.279
Hopefully. we will wage
war again soon. Boran Bey.

278
00:22:26.440 --> 00:22:27.879
Hopefully. hopefully.

279
00:22:28.560 --> 00:22:29.959
Still. your heart seems broken.

280
00:22:31.280 --> 00:22:32.799
Your troubles show on
your face. Boran Bey.

281
00:22:43.200 --> 00:22:44.439
Tell me. Boran Bey.

282
00:22:45.040 --> 00:22:47.879
Do these drums play
for good or for evil?

283
00:22:48.720 --> 00:22:49.719
O people!

284
00:22:52.360 --> 00:22:54.719
Osman Bey's brave son...

285
00:22:54.880 --> 00:22:57.519
His deputy Alaaddin Bey...

286
00:22:57.520 --> 00:22:59.319
Will hold a council
in the evening.

287
00:23:03.480 --> 00:23:04.719
Don't say you didn't hear.

288
00:23:08.520 --> 00:23:09.639
O people!

289
00:23:10.840 --> 00:23:13.079
Osman Bey's brave son...

290
00:23:13.080 --> 00:23:15.399
His deputy Alaaddin Bey...

291
00:23:15.400 --> 00:23:17.119
Will hold a council
in the evening.

292
00:23:17.120 --> 00:23:17.599
What council?

293
00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:19.639
Let no one remain unheard.

294
00:23:20.160 --> 00:23:22.839
Brother. sirs...

295
00:23:27.280 --> 00:23:29.239
My Osman Bey is very ill.

296
00:23:30.320 --> 00:23:34.519
If it weren't for
his delirium...

297
00:23:35.200 --> 00:23:36.399
In the land he lives in.

298
00:23:48.200 --> 00:23:50.359
That burden is my bey father's.

299
00:23:51.880 --> 00:23:54.639
Oh Allah. spare my
father for us. oh Lord.

300
00:24:03.120 --> 00:24:04.439
Father. father!

301
00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:06.519
Stop. stop.

302
00:24:06.560 --> 00:24:08.039
Osman Bey's brave son...

303
00:24:08.040 --> 00:24:10.799
Deputy Alaaddin Bey...

304
00:24:10.800 --> 00:24:11.919
Will gather the
council in the evening.

305
00:24:11.920 --> 00:24:13.719
Alaaddin Bey will
gather the council.

306
00:24:13.760 --> 00:24:15.359
This is his voice.

307
00:24:17.360 --> 00:24:21.279
My Sahin Sah and the
beys who trust him...

308
00:24:21.280 --> 00:24:22.679
Will support Alaaddin.

309
00:24:23.360 --> 00:24:25.639
If he stands firm...

310
00:24:25.640 --> 00:24:27.959
Then the beylik is
entrusted to Alaaddin.

311
00:24:28.680 --> 00:24:31.439
But the real task
falls to you now.

312
00:24:32.280 --> 00:24:33.559
Not only the beys'...

313
00:24:33.560 --> 00:24:36.359
But also the family's support
must be with Alaaddin.

314
00:24:38.160 --> 00:24:39.759
My mother's stance
has long been clear.

315
00:24:41.360 --> 00:24:42.479
She wants it to be Orhan.

316
00:24:43.400 --> 00:24:45.359
Fatma. you know. doesn't
go against my mother's word.

317
00:24:45.720 --> 00:24:46.359
Neither does Halime.

318
00:24:48.120 --> 00:24:51.439
Fatma marrying Yigit is
important for this reason.

319
00:24:52.080 --> 00:24:53.239
You need to help us.

320
00:24:54.560 --> 00:24:56.239
And you'll find a
solution for Halime too.

321
00:24:58.600 --> 00:25:01.439
You will be the future
mother of the state.

322
00:25:01.440 --> 00:25:05.639
That fire is in your
eyes. my daughter.

323
00:25:54.920 --> 00:25:56.639
Welcome. Commander Flavius.

324
00:26:00.360 --> 00:26:03.079
Welcome to the alliance...

325
00:26:03.080 --> 00:26:04.239
Flavius.

326
00:26:05.280 --> 00:26:07.399
Thank you for your
kind invitation...

327
00:26:07.840 --> 00:26:09.039
My mother. we are here.

328
00:26:16.160 --> 00:26:18.159
All the banners
gathered in one oba.

329
00:26:19.160 --> 00:26:20.639
I wouldn't want to be
in the enemy's shoes.

330
00:26:21.960 --> 00:26:23.999
He who sows the wind...

331
00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:25.159
Shall reap the whirlwind.

332
00:26:27.240 --> 00:26:31.679
This will be the main headquarters
for our attack against Kay..

333
00:26:32.000 --> 00:26:35.639
I wanted you to see the
men you'll be fighting with.

334
00:27:25.600 --> 00:27:27.039
I will talk to
Alaeddin and set off.

335
00:27:27.520 --> 00:27:28.359
They think I'm a child.

336
00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:30.359
May your path be clear. my Bey.

337
00:27:31.320 --> 00:27:32.199
My prayers are with you.

338
00:27:32.480 --> 00:27:33.439
May Allah help you.

339
00:27:36.960 --> 00:27:37.679
Come on.

340
00:27:40.120 --> 00:27:41.399
Did something happen
to my father. Halil?

341
00:27:41.800 --> 00:27:42.759
Osman Bey is the same. my Bey.

342
00:27:42.760 --> 00:27:44.959
But the plain is
not as you left it.

343
00:27:45.840 --> 00:27:46.999
Alaeddin Bey gathered the beys.

344
00:27:47.920 --> 00:27:48.999
A council was established
in the tent. my Bey.

345
00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:50.519
What council. Halil?

346
00:27:51.000 --> 00:27:51.759
A war council. my Bey.

347
00:27:54.880 --> 00:27:55.639
Alaeddin.

348
00:28:00.040 --> 00:28:04.479
The enemy's attack on my Orhan
Bey after the defeat in Bursa...

349
00:28:04.480 --> 00:28:08.879
It's only a matter of time before they
take advantage of Osman Bey's illness.

350
00:28:11.080 --> 00:28:15.319
Therefore. the immediate conquest
of Bursa is a more important matter...

351
00:28:15.320 --> 00:28:17.199
Let your ears hear what comes
out of your mouth. Sahin Sah Bey.

352
00:28:26.000 --> 00:28:28.999
While my father
lies ill inside...

353
00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:32.719
is there a more important
matter for this tribe than this?

354
00:28:34.920 --> 00:28:39.799
Instead of finding a cure for my father. you
gather for a feast and shout conquest slogans.

355
00:28:40.680 --> 00:28:41.479
Is that befitting of you?

356
00:28:44.640 --> 00:28:49.439
Everything necessary is being done
for Osman Bey's health. Orhan Bey.

357
00:28:49.840 --> 00:28:51.799
You will do that by staying
by his side. Alaeddin Bey.

358
00:28:53.040 --> 00:28:54.279
Not by holding a
feast beyond that.

359
00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:01.799
Both my father and the
state are entrusted to me.

360
00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:04.919
Rest assured.

361
00:29:07.880 --> 00:29:13.959
Osman Bey's health is certainly
very important for all of us.

362
00:29:13.960 --> 00:29:19.799
However. the survival of
our tribe is just as important.

363
00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:25.159
And that depends on the conquest
of Bursa as soon as possible.

364
00:29:25.680 --> 00:29:28.399
My Bey speaks the truth.
We have waited too long.

365
00:29:31.280 --> 00:29:33.439
You're fixated on
attacking Bursa.

366
00:29:34.760 --> 00:29:37.879
Don't you see? Now is not
the time for war with weapons...

367
00:29:37.880 --> 00:29:40.199
It is time to take precautions against
the alliance of reason and the enemy.

368
00:29:41.560 --> 00:29:45.879
Do your ears hear what comes
out of your mouth. Orhan Bey?

369
00:29:47.320 --> 00:29:51.999
You'll say. if you have a tongue.
let's make peace with the infidels.

370
00:29:52.920 --> 00:29:54.399
Consider it said. Sahin Sah Bey.

371
00:30:06.560 --> 00:30:08.719
The Karamanids will
come from this side...

372
00:30:09.720 --> 00:30:12.879
Germiyan from the south.
Karesi from the west...

373
00:30:15.000 --> 00:30:15.479
You are from the north.

374
00:30:22.040 --> 00:30:28.959
The Kayis. surrounded on all four
sides. will be trapped in a molehill...

375
00:30:28.960 --> 00:30:32.879
and will accept the
fate I have appointed.

376
00:30:35.760 --> 00:30:38.039
The fate that will
bring their end.

377
00:30:41.480 --> 00:30:44.159
Does a hopeful chicken ever
get slaughtered. Tulay Goz?

378
00:30:44.960 --> 00:30:47.479
I will never give
up tax revenue.

379
00:30:48.480 --> 00:30:53.239
I will leave a bey I trust in charge
of the Kayis and return to Sivas.

380
00:30:56.400 --> 00:30:58.519
If your goal isn't
to destroy them...

381
00:30:59.400 --> 00:31:00.999
what do you expect from me?

382
00:31:02.200 --> 00:31:07.879
When the time comes. you will
attack their headquarters so fiercely...

383
00:31:08.680 --> 00:31:12.759
you will break their arms
and wings so badly...

384
00:31:12.760 --> 00:31:16.199
that they will never. ever
dare to disobey my word again.

385
00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:17.879
They won't even dare.

386
00:31:21.600 --> 00:31:22.359
Consciousness!

387
00:31:24.120 --> 00:31:27.239
It is to put a stone on Kayl's
blessed path of conquest.

388
00:31:29.920 --> 00:31:33.879
Bursa. on one side. and the llkhanate. on
the other. will corner us and declare war.

389
00:31:34.560 --> 00:31:38.279
Is it fitting for Kayi to make
peace and submit. Orhan Bey?

390
00:31:38.560 --> 00:31:41.439
Will you fight all of them at once on
every front and cause the nation to perish?

391
00:31:42.760 --> 00:31:48.279
Half of the army is in Bursa. Who will be
able to reach everywhere in an all-out war?

392
00:31:50.160 --> 00:31:54.319
Once Bursa is taken. that army will
reach everywhere. by God's grace.

393
00:31:56.480 --> 00:32:00.879
Byzantium. the llkhanate. all
the beyliks have united for Bursa.

394
00:32:02.440 --> 00:32:06.839
If the way to break that unity is
through peace. then peace is the solution.

395
00:32:15.080 --> 00:32:19.199
To let someone else have Bursa.
which you couldn't take yourself...

396
00:32:19.600 --> 00:32:21.919
it must be hard. Orhan Bey.

397
00:32:27.560 --> 00:32:32.319
However. the only way to
break the unity of the infidels...

398
00:32:32.320 --> 00:32:34.999
Is to take Bursa through war.

399
00:32:36.520 --> 00:32:40.559
Waiting makes us look weak.
It whets the enemy's appetite.

400
00:32:43.080 --> 00:32:47.199
Our Orhan Bey has already
whetted their appetite enough.

401
00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:51.199
Hold on a moment. Avci Bey. It's as if
Sahin Sah Bey speaks incomplete words...

402
00:32:51.200 --> 00:32:53.079
and you rush to
complete them every time.

403
00:32:54.160 --> 00:32:54.639
Just hold on.

404
00:32:55.720 --> 00:32:58.679
I will defend the commander who
will lead us to conquest. Boran Bey.

405
00:33:00.160 --> 00:33:03.479
What about you? You defend the
commander who leads you to death.

406
00:33:06.200 --> 00:33:09.159
I went to these infidels myself.

407
00:33:10.160 --> 00:33:12.759
My Orhan Bey risked
his life to save me.

408
00:33:13.320 --> 00:33:16.239
He pulled me out. You
should first give him his due.

409
00:33:17.320 --> 00:33:19.079
Are their deeds in
Gemlik not enough?

410
00:33:19.080 --> 00:33:19.519
Enough.

411
00:33:21.920 --> 00:33:24.399
You are still arguing
about Orhan Bey. beys.

412
00:33:24.800 --> 00:33:26.879
Then end the
discussion. Alaeddin Bey.

413
00:33:27.280 --> 00:33:28.759
The command is yours.
and the decree is yours.

414
00:33:29.440 --> 00:33:31.799
Speak. Alaeddin.
Let everyone hear.

415
00:33:32.360 --> 00:33:35.039
Do you represent my Osman
Bey with sound judgment?

416
00:33:36.400 --> 00:33:38.799
Or by condoning Sahin
$Sah Bey's mistake?

417
00:34:07.200 --> 00:34:08.039
What?

418
00:34:11.440 --> 00:34:13.399
Osman's condition has worsened.

419
00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:17.999
Foolish man. He
will ruin all my plans.

420
00:34:18.440 --> 00:34:18.959
Fool!

421
00:34:24.520 --> 00:34:28.119
Tomorrow. a caravan will
depart from lnegol to Kay| Tribe.

422
00:34:28.800 --> 00:34:32.039
You will intercept that caravan
and bring all the ammunition here.

423
00:34:33.440 --> 00:34:34.919
It is your command.
Governor Demirtas.

424
00:34:35.440 --> 00:34:36.639
Keep your preparations tight.

425
00:34:37.520 --> 00:34:41.679
Osman's daughter. Fatma. will
be at the head of the caravan.

426
00:34:42.760 --> 00:34:43.719
As you command. sir.

427
00:34:44.640 --> 00:34:47.319
If it's suitable for you.
I'd like to take on this task.

428
00:34:53.280 --> 00:34:54.119
Reason?

429
00:34:56.800 --> 00:34:58.599
Osman is a personal matter.

430
00:35:00.400 --> 00:35:01.199
Let's say.

431
00:35:04.080 --> 00:35:04.919
Alright.

432
00:35:05.280 --> 00:35:05.879
But sir.

433
00:35:07.240 --> 00:35:08.519
Let's see your skill.

434
00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:11.639
Only...

435
00:35:11.640 --> 00:35:16.599
Don't you ever underestimate
the Turkmen girls. Flavius.

436
00:35:17.000 --> 00:35:19.599
Each one is as fierce
as a predatory tiger.

437
00:35:20.760 --> 00:35:21.519
Be careful.

438
00:35:22.040 --> 00:35:23.039
Don't worry at all.

439
00:35:25.520 --> 00:35:27.199
I will personally deal
with Osman's daughter.

440
00:35:30.720 --> 00:35:32.959
You will stay at the
head of the tribe.

441
00:35:33.800 --> 00:35:36.119
I will go to Bursa and
meet with $Sahin Sah.

442
00:35:38.720 --> 00:35:39.879
As you command. sir.

443
00:35:47.600 --> 00:35:52.359
When Bursa falls. all trade in
the region will fall into our hands.

444
00:35:52.640 --> 00:35:56.039
And then no one will
dare to stand against us.

445
00:35:56.800 --> 00:36:00.079
You underestimate the evil
alliance formed for Bursa. Aladdin.

446
00:36:01.760 --> 00:36:03.719
You tie the survival
of Kayi to an attack.

447
00:36:04.160 --> 00:36:06.279
Defeat is far from
us. Orhan Bey.

448
00:36:07.600 --> 00:36:09.559
You no longer command the army.

449
00:36:10.880 --> 00:36:12.919
You cannot stop
the Alps of Kay:.

450
00:36:13.600 --> 00:36:16.279
The conquest is
closer than ever.

451
00:36:20.360 --> 00:36:25.919
Bursa will be razed to the ground if
necessary under the command of Sahin Sah Bey.

452
00:36:30.240 --> 00:36:32.119
You will seek
your doom in error.

453
00:36:33.200 --> 00:36:34.959
I have neither my
permission nor my approval.

454
00:36:40.840 --> 00:36:41.879
Brother...

455
00:36:41.880 --> 00:36:45.319
Osman Bey's command
is the conquest of Bursa.

456
00:36:46.320 --> 00:36:51.159
If I am also his deputy. I
will do my duty. know that.

457
00:36:52.240 --> 00:36:56.359
Your duty is first and foremost
the future of the oba. Aladdin.

458
00:36:57.040 --> 00:36:58.799
What audacity. Orhan Bey!

459
00:36:59.560 --> 00:37:03.559
Are you defying not Aladdin Bey. but
my Osman Bey's absolute command?

460
00:37:03.960 --> 00:37:06.119
I am. Sahin Sah Bey. I am.

461
00:37:06.120 --> 00:37:10.119
Now. for the prosperity of
the oba. not for my brother...

462
00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:14.079
I would not hesitate for a
moment to defy even my father.

463
00:37:17.120 --> 00:37:18.719
From now on. my eyes are on you.

464
00:37:22.040 --> 00:37:23.959
Who is stronger.
the hand or the bey.

465
00:37:51.520 --> 00:37:55.559
You stay silent because he is your brother.
Don't you see that Aladdin Bey has gone astray?

466
00:37:55.560 --> 00:37:57.999
Don't miss it now.
Sahin Sah Bey.

467
00:37:58.200 --> 00:37:59.839
It is your Orhan Bey
who is truly running away.

468
00:37:59.880 --> 00:38:02.799
Permission. Hunter
Bey! Just permission.

469
00:38:03.400 --> 00:38:07.839
Look. these words you speak exceed
your limits and your neck. Be careful.

470
00:38:08.440 --> 00:38:09.079
Boran Bey!

471
00:38:09.320 --> 00:38:10.799
Enough! You've had
enough. I suppose!

472
00:38:17.920 --> 00:38:20.039
Boran Bey. Cerkutay Bey.

473
00:38:21.240 --> 00:38:26.279
I have assigned you to the headquarters
to give all your support to Sahin Sah Bey.

474
00:38:27.520 --> 00:38:28.399
He is your commander.

475
00:38:32.720 --> 00:38:36.999
And this is my decision. The army
will prepare for attack immediately.

476
00:38:39.160 --> 00:38:39.759
Immediately.

477
00:38:52.920 --> 00:38:53.839
La ilaha illallah.

478
00:38:55.440 --> 00:38:56.759
La ilaha illallah.

479
00:38:58.640 --> 00:38:59.759
What's wrong. crazy boy?

480
00:39:01.040 --> 00:39:05.439
Being a bey doesn't suit me.
Feast after feast. Not my thing at all.

481
00:39:06.040 --> 00:39:09.559
Of course not. Politics requires
wisdom. patience. Doesn't it?

482
00:39:10.320 --> 00:39:12.359
Can someone who wields words
like a weapon ever be a bey?

483
00:39:14.840 --> 00:39:18.839
My inside and outside are one.
brother. Let the words be for the beys.

484
00:39:19.440 --> 00:39:20.199
The battles are mine.

485
00:39:20.680 --> 00:39:24.479
It's a good thing. brother. it's a
good thing. Otherwise. in two days.

486
00:39:24.480 --> 00:39:26.599
the beys would devour
each other. Go on!

487
00:39:27.320 --> 00:39:27.599
My lord.

488
00:39:29.480 --> 00:39:30.159
Thank you.

489
00:39:32.080 --> 00:39:32.399
Send it.

490
00:39:37.000 --> 00:39:38.519
I heard you're good with horses.

491
00:39:39.560 --> 00:39:43.239
So they say. my lord. But |
know how to listen to them.

492
00:39:43.240 --> 00:39:49.639
Good. Don't you dare teach this to your foal.
Otherwise. this crazy horse will spoil their habits too.

493
00:39:54.320 --> 00:40:03.119
Alps! The task is ours again. Let
the young ones worry about Bursa.

494
00:40:04.520 --> 00:40:10.319
My concern is Osman Bey. My sister Fatma. Are you
willing to accompany me once more on the path of war?

495
00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:11.479
Once more on the path of war?

496
00:40:11.960 --> 00:40:13.439
We are with you
until the end. my lord.

497
00:40:13.440 --> 00:40:17.439
Thank you. The road is
long. the battle is near.

498
00:40:24.840 --> 00:40:25.399
Come on.

499
00:41:27.320 --> 00:41:29.519
Do you have any
orders. Fatma Hatun?

500
00:41:31.160 --> 00:41:35.799
After watering the horses. let them rest a
bit. Let them get their share from the pasture.

501
00:41:36.520 --> 00:41:37.679
It is your command. Fatma Hatun.

502
00:42:04.160 --> 00:42:06.559
What is the state of
those beautiful hands?

503
00:42:11.480 --> 00:42:13.759
You'll see if you get
slapped by Egyptian hands.

504
00:42:14.120 --> 00:42:14.479
Local.

505
00:42:15.160 --> 00:42:15.919
Tell me. who are you?

506
00:42:16.600 --> 00:42:18.759
Don't you see a strange merchant
who came to water his horse?

507
00:42:20.960 --> 00:42:24.319
The smell of water brought
us here. Like your caravan.

508
00:42:29.040 --> 00:42:29.999
Good thing he brought it.

509
00:42:30.960 --> 00:42:34.119
What are you after?
Where do you come from?

510
00:42:38.680 --> 00:42:39.439
If I'm going to kill you...

511
00:42:39.440 --> 00:42:40.319
at least tell me your name.

512
00:42:42.880 --> 00:42:45.479
So I know which angel killed me.

513
00:42:46.200 --> 00:42:47.879
I asked you where you come from.

514
00:42:48.640 --> 00:42:49.359
From Kay Tribe.

515
00:42:50.400 --> 00:42:50.919
I'm a merchant.

516
00:42:51.960 --> 00:42:53.799
I sold some fabric
to your women.

517
00:42:54.720 --> 00:42:55.199
However...

518
00:42:55.640 --> 00:42:56.799
business is a bit slow.

519
00:42:58.480 --> 00:43:00.359
It's wartime. you know.

520
00:43:02.800 --> 00:43:04.879
Since you come
from Kayi Tribe...

521
00:43:05.840 --> 00:43:06.479
tell me.

522
00:43:07.680 --> 00:43:08.559
What's the
situation in the tribe?

523
00:43:11.360 --> 00:43:13.919
If you lower the
knife from my throat...

524
00:43:13.920 --> 00:43:14.959
I'll tell you.

525
00:43:26.280 --> 00:43:27.199
Speak.

526
00:43:31.560 --> 00:43:33.639
Things in the tribe are more
chaotic than I've ever seen.

527
00:43:34.360 --> 00:43:35.519
What are you talking about?

528
00:43:36.400 --> 00:43:37.559
What's chaotic about it?

529
00:43:38.280 --> 00:43:39.839
Osman Bey dismissed Orhan Bey.

530
00:43:40.840 --> 00:43:42.399
He replaced him
with $Sahin $Sah Bey.

531
00:43:43.080 --> 00:43:43.679
What?

532
00:43:48.320 --> 00:43:49.239
Moreover...

533
00:43:49.240 --> 00:43:50.879
when I left. I wanted
to see Osman Bey.

534
00:43:50.880 --> 00:43:51.999
Osman Bey's
condition was not good.

535
00:43:53.360 --> 00:43:54.239
They say he's gravely ill.

536
00:43:59.880 --> 00:44:00.679
Allah...

537
00:44:00.680 --> 00:44:03.199
protect my Osman Bey.

538
00:44:05.760 --> 00:44:07.519
And all the Kayis too.

539
00:44:09.800 --> 00:44:12.879
I'll kill you here. you'll be
food for wolves and birds.

540
00:44:13.440 --> 00:44:14.359
What's wrong with my father?

541
00:44:20.280 --> 00:44:21.079
Are you...

542
00:44:21.880 --> 00:44:23.119
Osman Bey's daughter?

543
00:44:23.120 --> 00:44:26.239
I asked you what's
wrong with my father.

544
00:44:34.160 --> 00:44:35.319
Fatma Hatun. stop!

545
00:44:37.840 --> 00:44:38.239
Tell me.

546
00:44:40.840 --> 00:44:42.639
Tell me what's
wrong with my father?

547
00:44:43.680 --> 00:44:45.439
They call it something
else. not gout.

548
00:44:48.520 --> 00:44:49.479
What has befallen him?

549
00:45:04.880 --> 00:45:05.719
Fatma...

550
00:45:11.600 --> 00:45:12.359
forgot.

551
00:45:21.160 --> 00:45:22.839
My name...

552
00:45:22.840 --> 00:45:23.879
is Akgohora.

553
00:45:26.360 --> 00:45:29.719
Forgive me. I gave you bad news.

554
00:45:37.760 --> 00:45:39.279
Come on. come on!

555
00:46:00.480 --> 00:46:03.719
Tell the rye growers to move
before the caravan sets off.

556
00:46:04.120 --> 00:46:06.319
However. I want that girl alive.

557
00:46:08.800 --> 00:46:09.559
Do you understand?

558
00:46:10.880 --> 00:46:11.359
Act accordingly.

559
00:47:05.040 --> 00:47:05.959
The tracks are fresh. my Bey.

560
00:47:07.200 --> 00:47:07.879
They just passed.

561
00:47:21.560 --> 00:47:22.399
What did you see. my Bey?

562
00:47:26.080 --> 00:47:29.679
The tracks of the caravan are mixed
with the tracks of the horses' sisters.

563
00:47:31.840 --> 00:47:33.479
But these tracks are different.

564
00:47:35.480 --> 00:47:36.559
Not ours.

565
00:47:37.760 --> 00:47:38.679
They're after them.

566
00:47:41.160 --> 00:47:43.519
They'll take the
caravan animals to water.

567
00:47:45.320 --> 00:47:46.479
If we go by road. we'll be late.

568
00:47:47.400 --> 00:47:48.759
We'll go through
the forest. come on.

569
00:47:54.880 --> 00:47:56.439
Come on. come on!

570
00:48:09.160 --> 00:48:09.519
Come on!

571
00:48:27.720 --> 00:48:28.759
What's wrong. Yigit Bey?

572
00:48:29.880 --> 00:48:31.519
I'm fine. Fatma Hatun.

573
00:48:35.120 --> 00:48:36.999
My father sent me for
the safety of the caravan.

574
00:48:37.480 --> 00:48:37.959
What is it?

575
00:48:39.480 --> 00:48:41.839
After my brother was dismissed. did it fall
to your father to think about these things?

576
00:48:46.320 --> 00:48:47.159
How is my father?

577
00:48:59.600 --> 00:49:01.719
They say bad news
travels fast. but...

578
00:49:03.840 --> 00:49:05.279
you clearly haven't heard.

579
00:49:06.960 --> 00:49:10.119
Fatma Hatun. my Osman
Bey's condition has worsened.

580
00:49:16.920 --> 00:49:18.839
The square is first
the Caglars'. then ours.

581
00:49:21.760 --> 00:49:23.839
My Osman Bey has
overcome many troubles.

582
00:49:24.840 --> 00:49:26.039
You should keep
your heart at ease.

583
00:49:26.720 --> 00:49:28.159
He will overcome this
calamity too. God willing.

584
00:49:29.280 --> 00:49:29.919
He will overcome it.

585
00:49:31.200 --> 00:49:32.879
Of course. he will overcome
it with Allah's permission.

586
00:49:34.000 --> 00:49:34.759
My father is strong.

587
00:49:35.760 --> 00:49:36.159
God willing.

588
00:49:43.200 --> 00:49:44.119
Attack!

589
00:51:20.480 --> 00:51:21.879
Attack!

590
00:51:48.320 --> 00:51:48.919
Yigit!

591
00:51:54.760 --> 00:51:56.239
We're retreating!

592
00:51:56.600 --> 00:51:59.479
No! I can't leave the caravan!

593
00:52:00.000 --> 00:52:02.679
Come on. we're
retreating. them! Come on!

594
00:52:04.480 --> 00:52:05.039
Come on!

595
00:52:09.240 --> 00:52:13.799
These Caglars are good warriors. It
took even less time than I expected.

596
00:52:16.560 --> 00:52:18.799
Let them deal with
those left behind.

597
00:52:20.000 --> 00:52:21.599
Let's go and take the caravan.

598
00:52:34.280 --> 00:52:35.119
My daughter!

599
00:52:35.800 --> 00:52:36.639
Say hello to your owner.

600
00:52:42.680 --> 00:52:43.519
No. my daughter.

601
00:52:45.280 --> 00:52:46.359
We couldn't make
her laugh. my lady.

602
00:52:51.920 --> 00:52:55.319
I've been around horses
for so many years. but...

603
00:52:55.800 --> 00:52:58.039
I've never seen such a
brave one before. mashallah.

604
00:52:59.000 --> 00:53:03.279
If my Bey approves. I would like to see
this brave one by my side. Halime Hatun.

605
00:53:04.560 --> 00:53:05.999
He whispers to horses. it seems.

606
00:53:06.960 --> 00:53:08.319
Not whispering. Aykut Sergeant.

607
00:53:09.200 --> 00:53:11.959
A horse knows its owner's heart.
Isn't that right. Halime Hatun?

608
00:53:13.480 --> 00:53:16.559
Let my father get well. I'll
talk to him. Aykut Sergeant.

609
00:53:17.200 --> 00:53:18.359
Thank you. thank
you. Halime Hatun.

610
00:53:21.280 --> 00:53:25.159
I saw the bond my mother
and father had with their horses.

611
00:53:26.400 --> 00:53:28.439
There would be such a state
between them and their horses that...

612
00:53:28.920 --> 00:53:32.239
I would understand with a glance.
it would calm down in a breath.

613
00:53:34.000 --> 00:53:35.799
I haven't had such a horse yet.

614
00:53:37.440 --> 00:53:39.759
Perhaps you haven't found anyone
who understands you yet. Halime Hatun.

615
00:53:42.400 --> 00:53:47.399
Horses are like people. They only become companions
when they find someone with the same heart.

616
00:54:03.600 --> 00:54:08.479
Osman Bey's horse is always restless
these days. It must sense its owner too.

617
00:54:12.160 --> 00:54:15.439
I always knew my father's heart
to be unshakable like mountains.

618
00:54:18.880 --> 00:54:22.039
Now if that mountain shakes...

619
00:54:22.040 --> 00:54:24.239
Even ifithe mountain shakes. if its
roots are strong. it won't collapse.

620
00:54:25.680 --> 00:54:27.479
Osman Bey's roots are you.

621
00:54:28.840 --> 00:54:30.799
They say fathers get
strength from their children.

622
00:54:35.000 --> 00:54:38.079
Anyway. I came to get my horse.

623
00:54:39.480 --> 00:54:42.279
You can take it. your horse
is ready. Halime Hatun.

624
00:54:43.000 --> 00:54:47.239
No. it's not ready. It still doesn't
listen. it's unpleasant and insensitive.

625
00:54:49.280 --> 00:54:51.359
It won't go against the word
of its owner. whom I know.

626
00:54:55.280 --> 00:54:59.479
What do you say. Halime
Hatun? Will you give it a chance?

627
00:55:06.880 --> 00:55:10.679
Let's give it a chance then.
You can bring it to the parliament.

628
00:55:40.800 --> 00:55:44.359
His wife. my Bey. has started gathering the
army. She intends to declare war on the Kay:.

629
00:55:46.200 --> 00:55:48.119
But that means my
father and I decided.

630
00:55:49.080 --> 00:55:51.799
Things are quite complicated here
too. Osman Bey is on his deathbed.

631
00:55:52.280 --> 00:55:53.559
Alaeddin is in charge.

632
00:55:54.160 --> 00:55:54.599
What about Orhan?

633
00:55:55.160 --> 00:55:59.279
Orhan has no duty.
The pot is boiling in Kay!.

634
00:56:00.480 --> 00:56:05.519
They're close to falling into their graves.
The time will come. Isa. the time will come.

635
00:56:07.040 --> 00:56:08.079
Now go without
anyone seeing you.

636
00:56:30.680 --> 00:56:32.199
These are ours. come on.

637
00:56:47.960 --> 00:56:49.119
Stop. stop.

638
00:56:50.680 --> 00:56:51.559
Don't let go.

639
00:57:02.000 --> 00:57:06.159
What I heard at the feast is
a sign of discord. gelin hatun.

640
00:57:06.840 --> 00:57:10.959
If this continues. what those who put
my Osman In this state want will happen.

641
00:57:11.680 --> 00:57:14.199
Orhan will break
this game. I know.

642
00:57:15.120 --> 00:57:18.639
That vile physician died. but
we have the end of the rope.

643
00:57:19.560 --> 00:57:24.719
To be honest. I thought you'd be
rowing in vain. But you surprised me.

644
00:57:25.840 --> 00:57:29.279
Finally. your stubbornness
paid off. gelin hatun. Thank you.

645
00:57:32.120 --> 00:57:35.479
As my father always says.
see the good in the bad.

646
00:57:36.480 --> 00:57:39.519
Perhaps this pain will
teach us to trust each other.

647
00:57:44.960 --> 00:57:45.559
Alaeddin?

648
00:57:47.680 --> 00:57:48.879
What are these for?

649
00:57:51.920 --> 00:57:52.919
My father...

650
00:57:59.200 --> 00:58:00.879
cannot endure this much longer.

651
00:58:07.000 --> 00:58:09.279
Alaeddin. what will you do?

652
00:58:15.360 --> 00:58:17.639
I will clean the dirty
blood from his wounds.

653
00:58:19.760 --> 00:58:20.599
You all leave.

654
00:58:28.240 --> 00:58:28.959
Come on. mother.

655
00:58:37.040 --> 00:58:39.239
Give it to me. give it to me.

656
00:58:47.400 --> 00:58:48.399
In the name of Allah. the Most
Gracious. the Most Merciful.

657
00:58:54.800 --> 00:58:58.959
I will make you well. father.
You will be well. God willing.

658
00:59:00.400 --> 00:59:01.439
My lion father.

659
00:59:02.960 --> 00:59:04.319
My lion father.

660
00:59:12.760 --> 00:59:13.839
In the name of Allah. the Most
Gracious. the Most Merciful.

661
00:59:24.760 --> 00:59:28.839
He is entrusted to Alaeddin
Bey. My father will be well.

662
00:59:33.040 --> 00:59:33.559
Mother.

663
00:59:35.440 --> 00:59:36.679
How is my father?

664
00:59:38.200 --> 00:59:42.319
Alaeddin is with him. With all our
efforts. he will get better. God willing.

665
00:59:43.880 --> 00:59:48.159
Mashallah. Alaeddin Bey is both at the head of the beylic
and he does not leave his father alone for a moment.

666
00:59:48.160 --> 00:59:49.959
> Does not leave his
father alone for a moment.

667
00:59:50.600 --> 00:59:51.239
Always.

668
00:59:52.160 --> 00:59:55.359
So many things cannot
be handled with self-will.

669
00:59:55.960 --> 00:59:58.159
Who is self-willed? Say
what you mean. Dilara Hatun.

670
00:59:58.600 --> 01:00:01.479
The Bey got what he hoped for for
years. What is your problem now?

671
01:00:02.640 --> 01:00:03.839
I don't know Dilara
Hatun's problem.

672
01:00:03.840 --> 01:00:07.839
But ever since Alaeddin took
office. why don't you smile. Munifer?

673
01:00:08.800 --> 01:00:10.199
Is this brotherhood?

674
01:00:10.520 --> 01:00:14.639
Osman Bey struggles for his life
inside. Why do you speak like this?

675
01:00:15.720 --> 01:00:20.199
Are we worthy of this anger just because
Alaeddin Bey and Sahin $Sah Bey carry the trust?

676
01:00:20.840 --> 01:00:22.839
Won't our peace be disturbed
like this. Malhun Hatun?

677
01:00:23.080 --> 01:00:23.759
Patience.

678
01:00:24.160 --> 01:00:28.079
Mind your words. Dilara Hatun. The
peace of Kay|. the unity of my sons.

679
01:00:28.080 --> 01:00:29.559
and their lineage continue.

680
01:00:31.160 --> 01:00:36.519
They are our two wings. If they
lean towards wrong winds. I will never

681
01:00:36.520 --> 01:00:37.559
allow it.

682
01:00:38.040 --> 01:00:39.519
Alaeddin never
leans towards wrong.

683
01:00:39.520 --> 01:00:42.839
Enough. Gonca!
Enough. it's over now.

684
01:00:57.480 --> 01:01:01.679
Alaeddin. father
will get better. right?

685
01:01:32.520 --> 01:01:44.119
My father!

686
01:02:05.160 --> 01:02:05.799
Yigit!

687
01:02:15.360 --> 01:02:15.999
Hatun!

688
01:02:17.080 --> 01:02:17.679
Yigit!

689
01:02:19.480 --> 01:02:20.119
Hatun!

690
01:02:21.040 --> 01:02:21.519
Brother!

691
01:02:24.760 --> 01:02:26.639
There's no Yigit without
a wound. right. Yigit. huh?

692
01:02:27.960 --> 01:02:31.359
That's right. my Orhan Bey.
My two mothers in battle.

693
01:02:33.520 --> 01:02:34.519
What kind of place is it?

694
01:02:38.960 --> 01:02:39.839
Your aunt. Yigit Bey.

695
01:02:45.000 --> 01:02:45.679
Brother.

696
01:02:49.080 --> 01:02:53.519
Fatma. go to the oba immediately.
Take Yigit too. Go quickly.

697
01:02:54.200 --> 01:02:56.959
Tell me what happened. I'll
go after the caravan. Okay?

698
01:02:57.360 --> 01:02:59.559
Okay. Brother. my father?

699
01:03:00.560 --> 01:03:03.719
In his tent. The sons
are also after their duty.

700
01:03:04.640 --> 01:03:05.959
Thanks be to Allah.

701
01:03:05.960 --> 01:03:09.719
I'm going after the caravan.
Either I'll find a cure for my father.

702
01:03:10.240 --> 01:03:11.639
or I'll take their heads.

703
01:03:12.480 --> 01:03:15.039
Come on! Get ready. come on!

704
01:03:28.800 --> 01:03:31.719
Oh mother. oh! She
didn't even let me speak.

705
01:03:33.240 --> 01:03:36.759
She didn't have eyes to see
Nilufer. How will she defend her now?

706
01:03:36.760 --> 01:03:40.959
Oh. if my Osman Bey dies. The
pillar of this beylik will collapse.

707
01:03:41.400 --> 01:03:43.239
If they are like this already...

708
01:03:43.240 --> 01:03:45.439
May Allah forbid. Dilara Hatun.

709
01:03:45.800 --> 01:03:50.359
Yes. Oh Mahun. She says she doesn't
differentiate between children. but...

710
01:03:50.360 --> 01:03:56.119
She wants Orhan for the post. And prepares
Nilufer for her place. For state motherhood.

711
01:03:56.880 --> 01:04:02.839
The beylik is Alaeddin's right. All beys see
and know it. And my father's wish is this too.

712
01:04:02.840 --> 01:04:08.159
Yes. Yes. but look. she squeezed
it in between two sentences again.

713
01:04:08.560 --> 01:04:11.039
She keeps talking about the lineage
of my children. She's talking about you.

714
01:04:18.680 --> 01:04:27.399
Let me tell you. This is why she wanted
to marry Alaeddin off from the beginning.

715
01:04:28.160 --> 01:04:31.159
To show Orhan as the
sole heir of this principality.

716
01:04:31.800 --> 01:04:34.279
Otherwise. doesn't the
deceased know your love?

717
01:04:34.280 --> 01:04:40.679
That Alaeddin would not marry without your
consent. even for the sake of a position?

718
01:04:45.600 --> 01:04:48.159
I will ruin that
game. Dilara Hatun.

719
01:04:49.480 --> 01:04:51.919
Call Colpan. I will get to know
who she is and what she is.

720
01:04:53.800 --> 01:04:56.319
I knew you would
make this decision.

721
01:04:58.080 --> 01:05:00.359
I already sent word.
She will come today.

722
01:05:02.360 --> 01:05:03.959
This matter will end.

723
01:05:06.440 --> 01:05:11.639
Alaeddin. my Ali will have a
child. He will be the Bey of Kay!.

724
01:05:43.240 --> 01:05:48.279
Fatma Hatun escaped today.
We will surely meet again.

725
01:05:51.320 --> 01:05:54.479
I will take the caravan. You take
the soldiers and ambush the road.

726
01:05:55.360 --> 01:05:57.519
If you encounter
anyone. show no mercy.

727
01:06:02.160 --> 01:06:03.079
Let's go.

728
01:06:07.160 --> 01:06:07.599
Come on.

729
01:06:18.560 --> 01:06:22.919
The infidels on one side. and the llkhanids
and beys on the other. come upon us.

730
01:06:25.040 --> 01:06:29.519
We will be in a difficult situation. I will
move my leg and some of the horses to the south.

731
01:06:34.840 --> 01:06:37.919
Alaeddin. my leg has not
been chosen as the leader yet.

732
01:06:40.600 --> 01:06:42.759
I will choose a suitable person.

733
01:06:44.360 --> 01:06:48.919
Mother. it's not right to change horses while
crossing the bridge. Perhaps it's not my place.

734
01:06:49.640 --> 01:06:52.079
But I say Halime
should continue her duty.

735
01:06:52.640 --> 01:06:55.999
You're right. Gonca.
It's not her place.

736
01:06:57.600 --> 01:06:59.679
Halime made a
mistake. she will pay for it.

737
01:07:00.440 --> 01:07:03.399
Mother. this punishment you're
giving is not for me. it's for the army.

738
01:07:03.920 --> 01:07:07.639
You shouldn't have thought about this before
defying my word and plotting in secret.

739
01:07:08.560 --> 01:07:10.479
It's over. you are no
longer the head sister.

740
01:07:12.840 --> 01:07:18.239
I respect your word greatly.
But not now. mother. not now.

741
