790
01:11:30.560 --> 01:11:33.879
Either I will find this tunnel.
or this tunnel will find my grave.

791
01:11:46.800 --> 01:11:51.879
Before going to the camp. I called you to come to Bursa and see the
preparations for the big attack we will make soon. so you would be pleased.

792
01:11:51.880 --> 01:11:56.599
I called you to come to Bursa and see the preparations for
the big attack we will make soon. so you would be pleased.

793
01:11:58.440 --> 01:12:01.559
However. I believe what I
hear. not what I see. Sarhoz.

794
01:12:02.400 --> 01:12:05.119
Sahinsah prevented you
