800
01:12:32.200 --> 01:12:36.879
Osman must live. Only
then will discord arise in Kay..

801
01:12:38.400 --> 01:12:41.359
If he dies. they will all unite.

802
01:12:56.400 --> 01:13:02.559
Either Sahingah will lift that siege
peacefully. or we will eliminate Kay forever.

803
