859
01:19:39.240 --> 01:19:41.799
Long live my Osman Bey!

860
01:19:42.080 --> 01:19:43.519
Long live my Osman Bey!

861
01:19:43.560 --> 01:19:44.479
Long live my Alaaddin Bey!

862
01:19:44.480 --> 01:19:45.559
Long live my Alaaddin Bey!

863
01:19:45.560 --> 01:19:46.119
Long live my Alaaddin Bey!

