01:31:39.000 --> 01:31:43.439
This headquarters will be spoils of
war for you. Along with its contents.

965
01:31:43.640 --> 01:31:48.359
Next time. you will enter this headquarters
as a victorious commander. Temurtas.

966
01:31:56.760 --> 01:32:02.999
I told you. I told you. They would eventually learn of
my Bey's illness and seize the opportunity to attack.

967
01:32:05.440 --> 01:32:08.119
I will go and speak with my
Bey Alaeddin immediately.

968
01:32:09.120 --> 01:32:14.039
I will ask him to send the entire army
to Bursa. I will finish this in one go.

969
01:32:15.720 --> 01:32:18.439
The headquarters is entrusted to you.
Boran Bey. along with Cerkutay Bey.

970
01:32:36.000 --> 01:32:41.879
My father. my lion father.

971
01:33:22.480 --> 01:33:34.319
My mind and heart are at war. brother.
My heart. my prayers are always with you.

972
01:33:46.280 --> 01:33:54.999
But this seal is so
heavy. brother. so heavy.

973
01:34:02.560 --> 01:34:09.439
At that time. if you speak of justice.
the voice of brotherhood is silenced.

974
01:34:19.560 --> 01:34:33.999
Oh Allah. I will keep them together.
You. my Lord. grant us my father.

975
01:34:36.280 --> 01:34:38.439
Grant us my father.

976
01:35:06.920 --> 01:35:08.719
Hurry. half of it is bad.

977
01:35:09.880 --> 01:35:12.839
Fatima. I found Fatima's end.

978
01:35:14.200 --> 01:35:17.999
We'll make it. Yigit Bey. You'll
be fine. don't strain yourself.

979
01:35:18.800 --> 01:35:22.759
I'm fine. I'm very fine.

980
01:35:25.560 --> 01:35:29.839
No. he won't endure. he'll reach
the oba. We'll get the wound too.

981
01:35:30.640 --> 01:35:31.039
Stop!

982
01:35:37.680 --> 01:35:38.439
Fatima!

983
01:35:43.560 --> 01:35:45.359
Quickly light a fire. come on!

984
01:35:57.920 --> 01:35:59.959
You'll wrestle with
Azrael instead of me.

985
01:36:02.000 --> 01:36:10.159
What is this wound?
Fatima. you...

986
01:36:17.160 --> 01:36:18.999
O Healer. O Healer. O Healer.

987
01:36:32.200 --> 01:36:33.639
Our blood has stopped.

988
01:36:36.080 --> 01:36:37.719
But his fever
is still very high.

989
01:36:39.280 --> 01:36:41.439
Come on. aunt. to the oba!

990
01:37:52.640 --> 01:37:54.359
We shouldn't have
sent my Bey alone.

991
01:37:54.480 --> 01:37:59.279
Then. my Bey knows what to do.

992
01:38:49.920 --> 01:38:55.559
Oh. my lion. my beautiful son.

993
01:39:00.920 --> 01:39:01.799
Bey father!

994
01:39:06.320 --> 01:39:07.159
My Colpan!

995
01:39:08.400 --> 01:39:09.519
My dear child.

996
01:39:13.200 --> 01:39:15.079
What brings you here?

997
01:39:16.480 --> 01:39:19.399
Didar Hatun called me to
help Gonca Hatun. father.

998
01:39:20.320 --> 01:39:21.759
If you allow it.

999
01:39:23.920 --> 01:39:25.239
To Gonca Hatun?

1000
01:39:29.280 --> 01:39:35.119
Didar Hatun is such a smart
woman. she never wastes her mind.

1001
01:39:37.440 --> 01:39:39.279
What do you mean. father?

1002
01:39:40.080 --> 01:39:43.559
My beautiful daughter.
the light of my eyes.

1003
01:39:44.520 --> 01:39:50.279
If you act smart. I'll tell Alaaddin Bey
that we'll arrange a wedding for you.

1004
01:39:57.680 --> 01:40:01.159
Open your eyes. your luck
will turn. my beautiful girl.

1005
01:40:32.360 --> 01:40:36.039
Don't worry. mother. I'm
here. I'm with my father.

1006
01:40:36.200 --> 01:40:38.239
She raves about
Kasim and Suleyman.

1007
01:40:38.240 --> 01:40:42.039
If I go and bring them. maybe
hearing their voices will be a cure.

1008
01:40:42.200 --> 01:40:43.279
Shall I go and bring them?

1009
01:40:43.760 --> 01:40:44.719
Bring them. mother. bring them.

1010
01:41:02.640 --> 01:41:06.199
When did you go to the headquarters
and when did you return. Sahinsah Bey?

1011
01:41:07.120 --> 01:41:12.559
Those who met me at the headquarters
were Sarhoz and Temurtas. Alaaddin.

1012
01:41:12.920 --> 01:41:13.559
Allah Allah!

1013
01:41:15.280 --> 01:41:18.199
So they can enter and leave
Bursa that easily. can they?

1014
01:41:18.920 --> 01:41:19.639
Yes.

1015
01:41:21.200 --> 01:41:23.959
Yes. what do they say?
Tell me. Sahinsah Bey.

1016
01:41:25.400 --> 01:41:29.279
They threaten that if you attack
Bursa. you won't have a tomorrow.

1017
01:41:30.160 --> 01:41:33.999
We must make today hell for
those who threaten us with tomorrow.

1018
01:41:34.720 --> 01:41:37.079
Alright. I gave you the
authority. go and take Bursa.

1019
01:41:37.560 --> 01:41:41.439
Not authority. I also
want the rest of the army.

1020
01:41:43.000 --> 01:41:47.599
For absolute victory. we must
send everything we have to Bursa.

1021
01:41:47.600 --> 01:41:50.079
That won't happen. Sahinsah Bey.

1022
01:41:51.080 --> 01:41:54.639
Shifting all troops to Bursa
means abandoning all borders.

1023
01:41:56.520 --> 01:42:01.279
Not taking Bursa today means
shifting the entire army to the border.

1024
01:42:04.560 --> 01:42:08.839
The enemy has been emboldened.
they know of Osman Bey's illness.

1025
01:42:09.640 --> 01:42:14.119
They see Orhan Bey's rebellion.
and the division that will arise in Kay:.

1026
01:42:15.120 --> 01:42:19.519
Without giving them a chance
to breathe. or to or anize...

1027
01:42:19.680 --> 01:42:23.439
It is imperative to take Bursa
in one go with all our might.

1028
01:42:24.360 --> 01:42:28.039
Thus. we can defend our
borders with our entire army.

1029
01:42:35.720 --> 01:42:36.799
Prepare!

1030
01:42:41.120 --> 01:42:43.599
The soldiers we sent to set
up water haven't returned.

1031
01:42:44.520 --> 01:42:45.239
Something is wrong.

1032
01:42:48.840 --> 01:42:50.039
Prepare my horse!

1033
01:43:06.080 --> 01:43:07.039
What are you after?

1034
01:43:08.000 --> 01:43:12.759
Shhh. I wouldn't recommend it.

1035
01:43:58.400 --> 01:43:59.639
Come on. stay fast. come on!

1036
01:44:00.960 --> 01:44:01.679
Come on!

1037
01:44:03.280 --> 01:44:06.999
What are you doing. son of a Bey?
Are you taking out your anger on straw?

1038
01:44:08.520 --> 01:44:12.319
I'm thinking. When a person makes a mistake.
they are punished. Isn't that right. Dursun Aga?

1039
01:44:12.920 --> 01:44:16.919
Yes. indeed. Both the Bey and the
alp pay the price for their mistakes.

1040
01:44:18.680 --> 01:44:23.679
But my father didn't make a mistake. Why is my
grandfather punishing my father for no reason?

1041
01:44:25.080 --> 01:44:29.959
It is not easy to understand the decision of the
lords. princes. A lord rules not with his heart.

1042
01:44:30.920 --> 01:44:31.679
but with his mind.

1043
01:44:32.880 --> 01:44:38.919
My father is always at the camp. He
rarely comes to us. We rarely come to him.

1044
01:44:39.560 --> 01:44:42.919
But we are never sad about this.
Because my father strived for Bursa.

1045
01:44:43.800 --> 01:44:46.319
Does my grandfather not see
my father's effort? Is this fair?

1046
01:44:47.200 --> 01:44:53.319
I know. My grandfather no longer loves my father.
He doesn't love us either. Right. brother?

1047
01:44:53.320 --> 01:44:55.479
Yeah. he doesn't.

1048
01:44:56.160 --> 01:44:58.279
Suleyman. Kasim.

1049
01:45:06.440 --> 01:45:10.319
While your grandfather is on his
sickbed. missing you and rambling. do you

1050
01:45:10.320 --> 01:45:12.159
complain about him here?

1051
01:45:24.160 --> 01:45:27.159
This is all because of
your incompetence. Hilfer.

1052
01:45:32.080 --> 01:45:34.839
A Byzantine commander
in the Cavdar tribe.

1053
01:45:37.400 --> 01:45:39.639
A prince who has fallen out of
favor due to the Bursa defeat.

1054
01:45:42.840 --> 01:45:44.679
Did you come to the
Cavdar tribe to die?

1055
01:45:45.760 --> 01:45:48.159
You speak as if the spring
is in your hand. Flavius.

1056
01:45:52.520 --> 01:45:58.599
And you speak as if this place is
filled with your men and not mine.

1057
01:45:59.640 --> 01:46:00.959
How do you know it isn't?

1058
01:46:04.680 --> 01:46:07.479
If you kill me. there's no way out of
here. and you know that very well.

1059
01:46:10.800 --> 01:46:12.559
You were going to stab
me in the back silently.

1060
01:46:14.920 --> 01:46:16.959
You'll regret not doing it.

1061
01:46:18.640 --> 01:46:23.159
Even if it's my enemy. stabbing
them in the back IS not in our book.

1062
01:46:24.240 --> 01:46:24.719
Is that so?

1063
01:46:37.280 --> 01:46:38.639
What's wrong. Malhun Hatun?

1064
01:46:40.920 --> 01:46:43.439
Your children will be
taken from you. bride.

1065
01:46:44.360 --> 01:46:45.559
Did they make a mistake?

1066
01:46:46.120 --> 01:46:47.799
It wasn't them who made
the mistake. it was you.

1067
01:46:48.800 --> 01:46:51.599
The children openly
criticize their grandfather.

1068
01:46:52.160 --> 01:46:53.799
The pillar of the
oba. its brain.

1069
01:46:54.400 --> 01:46:57.759
They are children. They say whatever
they hear. They don't understand.

1070
01:46:58.320 --> 01:47:01.519
If they don't understand.
they need to be told and taught.

1071
01:47:02.040 --> 01:47:02.919
By you.

1072
01:47:04.600 --> 01:47:09.999
A child who questions his ancestor's words will
disregard the state's rule when he grows up.

1073
01:47:11.400 --> 01:47:13.959
The word of the state is
not to be debated in a tent.

1074
01:47:13.960 --> 01:47:18.559
A whisper in the oba
turns into sedition tomorrow.

1075
01:47:19.560 --> 01:47:22.959
My children are loyal to their
ancestors and their grandfathers.

1076
01:47:24.280 --> 01:47:25.319
Their hearts are simply broken.

1077
01:47:27.680 --> 01:47:30.439
It's not the heart that's
broken. it's the order.

1078
01:47:31.320 --> 01:47:33.759
A bey's son must
hold his tongue.

1079
01:47:34.800 --> 01:47:36.999
They will be the
foundation of our state.

1080
01:47:39.200 --> 01:47:42.999
It is essential that Kasim
and Suleyman are educated.

1081
01:47:43.000 --> 01:47:44.839
They lack discipline.

1082
01:47:45.840 --> 01:47:49.479
I am taking care of my
children. Malhun Hatun.

1083
01:47:50.800 --> 01:47:51.759
It's clear.
daughter-in-law. it's clear.

1084
01:47:52.880 --> 01:47:55.279
But from now on. my
eyes will be on them.

1085
01:47:57.480 --> 01:48:00.199
If I hear of such
a situation again...

1086
01:48:00.200 --> 01:48:02.599
know from this moment on that...

1087
01:48:02.600 --> 01:48:05.999
I will discipline them. not you.

1088
01:48:44.080 --> 01:48:46.239
You tell me about these
hearts you've made.

1089
01:48:46.240 --> 01:48:47.159
What?

1090
01:48:48.960 --> 01:48:51.719
Is the person who killed my
brother with a spear saying this?

1091
01:48:52.920 --> 01:48:55.159
The son of the one who killed
my father in the Battle of Afyon.

1092
01:48:56.960 --> 01:48:59.399
Boran Bey told
you. tell me again.

1093
01:49:00.240 --> 01:49:01.719
We didn't kill your father.

1094
01:49:03.000 --> 01:49:05.439
You defend each other with lies.

1095
01:49:06.880 --> 01:49:09.559
We speak the truth at the
cost of our lives. Flavius.

1096
01:49:10.600 --> 01:49:13.199
I killed your brother.
Because we were at war.

1097
01:49:13.200 --> 01:49:20.639
And I will avenge
both of them. Orhan.

1098
01:49:21.200 --> 01:49:22.399
If you're going to take
it. take it honorably.

1099
01:49:23.680 --> 01:49:25.799
Not by secretly
poisoning my father.

1100
01:49:45.480 --> 01:49:49.719
For absolute victory. we must
send everything we have to Bursa.

1101
01:49:51.800 --> 01:49:55.319
This... this is a very big
decision. Sahinsah Bey.

1102
01:49:58.120 --> 01:50:01.239
It is necessary to consult
the lords of the border troops.

1103
01:50:02.200 --> 01:50:05.519
There is no time to spend
on a Toya meeting. Alaeddin.

1104
01:50:06.400 --> 01:50:09.039
The infidels are waiting
ready to fall upon us.

1105
01:50:10.280 --> 01:50:13.119
Ilhan will be at the tent's
door before the Beys.

1106
01:50:14.200 --> 01:50:16.119
The decree is yours.
and the command is yours.

1107
01:50:17.080 --> 01:50:18.479
Give the order. let's
finish this business.

1108
01:50:23.280 --> 01:50:24.119
What's wrong?

1109
01:50:24.680 --> 01:50:26.399
My Bey. the ammunition
caravan coming from Inegol...

1110
01:50:26.400 --> 01:50:27.439
What happened to the caravan?

1111
01:50:31.440 --> 01:50:32.919
What happened to
the caravan. I'll tell you?

1112
01:50:39.720 --> 01:50:40.159
Hold on!

1113
01:50:43.000 --> 01:50:45.639
I'm here. Yigit.
hold on. we're here.

1114
01:50:46.960 --> 01:50:48.799
Quickly. send word
to the healer. hurry!

1115
01:50:55.960 --> 01:50:56.799
To my throat...

1116
01:50:56.800 --> 01:50:58.679
Grin and bear it.

1117
01:50:59.600 --> 01:51:00.999
We're here. hold
on. don't talk. okay?

1118
01:51:05.360 --> 01:51:06.559
Han. where is the poison?

1119
01:51:12.760 --> 01:51:14.079
What poison are
you talking about?

1120
01:51:15.240 --> 01:51:17.999
The poison that is the
reason I haven't struck you yet.

1121
01:51:28.320 --> 01:51:29.399
I am wrong. Orhan.

1122
01:51:31.000 --> 01:51:32.119
And I have no
poisonous business.

1123
01:51:32.960 --> 01:51:35.999
We learned to fight face to
face. bravely. from our father.

1124
01:51:37.480 --> 01:51:39.999
If you have nothing to do with poison.
what are you doing where there is poison?

1125
01:51:44.240 --> 01:51:47.639
I came here to form an alliance
that will bury Kayi in history. Orhan.

1126
01:51:49.680 --> 01:51:51.399
Ilkhanid-Byzantine alliance.

1127
01:52:19.000 --> 01:52:19.719
Esma...

1128
01:52:19.720 --> 01:52:23.919
Keep an eye on the children. Let's
not give Malhun Hatun a reason to talk.

1129
01:52:24.280 --> 01:52:27.519
Gonca Hatun has changed the
duties of the women close to you.

1130
01:52:27.840 --> 01:52:29.919
My lady. you put so much
effort into establishing that order.

1131
01:52:30.800 --> 01:52:33.759
No one can waste your
efforts. I won't allow it.

1132
01:52:34.600 --> 01:52:36.079
Gonca's time will come too.

1133
01:52:41.920 --> 01:52:43.879
What happened again. aunt?

1134
01:52:44.360 --> 01:52:45.839
Don't you see what's
happening. Halime?

1135
01:52:45.840 --> 01:52:48.879
On one side Malhun
Hatun. on the other Gonca.

1136
01:52:50.040 --> 01:52:50.919
They keep bothering me.

1137
01:53:17.160 --> 01:53:19.439
What are you doing here. raider?

1138
01:53:21.080 --> 01:53:22.159
I'm talking to you.

1139
01:53:24.240 --> 01:53:25.159
Who are you?

1140
01:53:34.400 --> 01:53:40.079
There were commanders who said they would bury my
grandfather Ertugrul in Aleppo and my father Osman in Sogut.

1141
01:53:41.280 --> 01:53:43.159
None of their names
are remembered. Flavius.

1142
01:53:44.600 --> 01:53:46.999
But my brother's name...

1143
01:53:48.920 --> 01:53:51.319
your blood...

1144
01:53:51.320 --> 01:53:53.319
will be remembered
when it stains my sword.

1145
01:53:55.040 --> 01:53:55.519
Orhan.

1146
01:53:57.680 --> 01:54:00.239
I killed your brother
because we were at war.

1147
01:54:02.920 --> 01:54:04.919
The rules of war are clear.

1148
01:54:10.720 --> 01:54:12.319
We've been exposed.
Defend yourselves!

1149
01:54:39.760 --> 01:54:41.599
I guess we're at war.

1150
01:55:17.440 --> 01:55:18.359
Come on. horses.

1151
01:55:19.720 --> 01:55:20.319
Fatma.

1152
01:55:20.640 --> 01:55:22.039
Brother. I've
lost a lot of blood.

1153
01:55:22.560 --> 01:55:23.839
You. move to the
infirmary. come on.

1154
01:55:24.000 --> 01:55:24.439
My son.

1155
01:55:24.800 --> 01:55:25.799
Bring Taz. come on.

1156
01:55:26.040 --> 01:55:26.919
Come on. horses. come on.

1157
01:55:28.240 --> 01:55:29.319
Bring him here immediately.

1158
01:55:29.600 --> 01:55:29.879
Come on.

1159
01:55:30.080 --> 01:55:31.039
You too. quickly. come on.

1160
01:55:31.120 --> 01:55:32.159
Come on. my brave one. come.

1161
01:55:33.400 --> 01:55:34.079
Come on. my brave one.

1162
01:55:36.320 --> 01:55:36.919
My son.

1163
01:55:38.280 --> 01:55:39.519
To the infirmary.
quickly. come on.

1164
01:55:39.680 --> 01:55:39.999
Fatma.

1165
01:55:40.080 --> 01:55:40.439
Come on.

1166
01:55:40.760 --> 01:55:41.719
My Fatma. are you alright?

1167
01:55:42.160 --> 01:55:42.759
I'm fine.

1168
01:55:42.800 --> 01:55:43.079
My son.

1169
01:55:47.560 --> 01:55:49.319
Sahinsah Bey. you wait here.

1170
01:55:49.680 --> 01:55:49.999
Come on.

1171
01:55:51.200 --> 01:55:53.319
Who did this to my
son. Fatma Hatun?

1172
01:55:53.440 --> 01:55:54.439
They attacked the caravan.

1173
01:55:55.200 --> 01:55:57.199
If my brother Orhan hadn't
arrived. it would have been worse.

1174
01:55:57.360 --> 01:55:57.759
Orhan?

1175
01:55:58.520 --> 01:55:59.559
What was Orhan doing there?

1176
01:55:59.920 --> 01:56:00.799
Where is Orhan. Fatma?

1177
01:56:01.400 --> 01:56:02.119
He went after them.

1178
01:56:02.840 --> 01:56:04.599
Orhan Bey. Orhan Bey.

1179
01:56:05.200 --> 01:56:08.119
Again. he acts on his own
accord. again as he pleases.

1180
01:56:08.800 --> 01:56:11.319
He learned about the
raid but didn't tell us. huh?

1181
01:56:11.320 --> 01:56:13.039
What did he do when he
found out. Sahinsah Bey?

1182
01:56:13.440 --> 01:56:14.599
He went after
them and caught up.

1183
01:56:17.000 --> 01:56:20.759
If he had caught up. would my
son be in this state. Nilufer Hatun?

1184
01:56:21.360 --> 01:56:23.479
Don't you see my
son covered in blood?

1185
01:56:25.680 --> 01:56:27.599
Your Orhan is after heroism.

1186
01:56:27.880 --> 01:56:43.399
But look...

1187
01:56:43.400 --> 01:56:44.799
Today. one of us will die. Of a.

1188
01:56:55.840 --> 01:56:57.759
I came here to get
my father's cure.

1189
01:56:58.880 --> 01:57:00.239
I have no intention of
dying without getting it.

1190
01:57:01.480 --> 01:57:04.199
The only good deed I
will do for your father...

1191
01:57:04.200 --> 01:57:06.119
Would be to send
you to his side.

1192
01:57:24.480 --> 01:57:25.319
My lord!

1193
01:57:32.600 --> 01:57:33.919
The sword belongs
in its sheath. Flavius.

1194
01:57:35.800 --> 01:57:38.199
Let our revenge be
settled on the battlefield.

1195
01:57:40.040 --> 01:57:42.239
What I want is my father's cure.

1196
01:57:55.480 --> 01:57:57.159
Osman's best.

1197
01:57:58.160 --> 01:58:00.239
Oh. we were going
to come to you...

1198
01:58:00.840 --> 01:58:02.279
You have come to us.

1199
01:58:14.160 --> 01:58:15.199
An honorable man...

1200
01:58:15.640 --> 01:58:17.319
Does not sheathe his
sword before it is bloodied.

1201
01:58:19.280 --> 01:58:20.679
This is the battlefield!

1202
01:58:22.040 --> 01:58:22.639
And your grave!

1203
01:58:25.560 --> 01:58:26.079
Attack!

1204
01:58:31.320 --> 01:58:32.359
Alps!

1205
01:58:34.720 --> 01:58:34.999
Alps!

1206
01:59:03.200 --> 01:59:04.679
We will meet again. my son.

1207
01:59:06.960 --> 01:59:07.759
Flavius!

1208
01:59:13.000 --> 01:59:13.519
Halil!

1209
01:59:21.240 --> 01:59:22.519
Timurtas's best!

1210
01:59:23.720 --> 01:59:24.079
Go!

1211
01:59:24.720 --> 01:59:26.559
Let me go! I said let me go!

1212
01:59:27.360 --> 01:59:27.639
Where to?

1213
01:59:28.960 --> 01:59:31.079
Let go! Let go!

1214
01:59:33.960 --> 01:59:35.679
I will ask you once.

1215
01:59:36.760 --> 01:59:37.839
Where is my father's cure?

1216
01:59:38.280 --> 01:59:39.039
What are you talking about?

1217
01:59:44.120 --> 01:59:47.679
If you don't play games with
me. I'll burn you alive in that fire.

1218
01:59:50.280 --> 01:59:51.319
Timurtas will kill me.

1219
01:59:52.320 --> 01:59:54.319
He'll feed me to the wolves and
birds even if he doesn't kill me.

1220
01:59:54.720 --> 01:59:56.879
Do you think I
would let you live?

1221
01:59:57.720 --> 01:59:58.919
Stop! Stop!

1222
01:59:59.400 --> 02:00:00.239
Okay. I'll tell you.

1223
02:00:09.720 --> 02:00:10.519
But...

1224
02:00:10.520 --> 02:00:12.879
You poisoned my
father in various ways.

1225
02:00:13.440 --> 02:00:14.359
Hold on. my daughter.

1226
02:00:16.840 --> 02:00:18.679
What poison? I'm not a variety.

1227
02:00:27.400 --> 02:00:30.239
Fatma Hatun brought
Yigit. He was wounded.

1228
02:00:30.680 --> 02:00:31.279
Is my sister okay?

1229
02:00:31.720 --> 02:00:32.759
She's fine. thank God.

1230
02:00:33.280 --> 02:00:34.279
Thank goodness.

1231
02:00:35.080 --> 02:00:36.119
Just come here.

1232
02:00:42.480 --> 02:00:44.959
Tie his hands and feet nicely...

1233
02:00:45.760 --> 02:00:47.399
bring him here
without anyone seeing.

1234
02:00:48.920 --> 02:00:49.559
Indeed.

1235
02:00:53.560 --> 02:00:55.439
What if my Orhan hadn't arrived?

1236
02:00:56.000 --> 02:00:58.319
If he hadn't. neither I nor Yigit
Bey would have survived. mother.

1237
02:00:59.120 --> 02:01:00.239
May God protect us.

1238
02:01:03.000 --> 02:01:03.559
Sister!

1239
02:01:04.480 --> 02:01:05.039
My Halime!

1240
02:01:05.240 --> 02:01:05.599
Sister!

1241
02:01:07.320 --> 02:01:10.479
Sister. are you okay? Who
did this? How did this happen?

1242
02:01:10.680 --> 02:01:11.839
I'm fine. my
Halime. don't worry.

1243
02:02:58.000 --> 02:02:58.639
Orhan...

1244
02:02:58.640 --> 02:02:59.919
oh my Lord...

1245
02:03:01.000 --> 02:03:03.359
Your wisdom is unquestionable.

1246
02:03:05.120 --> 02:03:08.639
To the meaning of
this unbearable pain...

1247
02:03:10.280 --> 02:03:12.399
make me aware. oh my Lord.

1248
02:03:14.120 --> 02:03:15.719
Will this tribe...

1249
02:03:17.200 --> 02:03:18.199
flourish in a land
washed with my tears...

1250
02:03:19.160 --> 02:03:23.639
and Orhan's blood?

1251
02:03:25.080 --> 02:03:26.279
Yigit...

1252
02:03:28.040 --> 02:03:30.679
for what did I sacrifice you?

1253
02:03:33.000 --> 02:03:35.639
Speak. tell me. my son.

1254
02:03:37.680 --> 02:03:38.639
Don't be silent like this.

1255
02:03:59.920 --> 02:04:02.679
For what did I sacrifice you?

1256
02:04:04.080 --> 02:04:04.999
Speak...

1257
02:04:06.160 --> 02:04:07.679
you tell me. son.

1258
02:04:09.760 --> 02:04:10.359
Don't be silent...

1259
02:04:10.960 --> 02:04:12.039
don't be silent like that.

1260
02:04:15.280 --> 02:04:16.279
Osman?

1261
02:04:24.760 --> 02:04:25.479
Malhun.

1262
02:04:27.000 --> 02:04:28.399
What do you say. my Osman?

1263
02:04:33.080 --> 02:04:34.479
What is the situation...

1264
02:04:34.480 --> 02:04:35.159
what is it?

1265
02:04:37.680 --> 02:04:40.159
Are my children well?

1266
02:04:41.400 --> 02:04:43.199
They are all well.

1267
02:04:43.960 --> 02:04:45.359
Orhan and Alaeddin...

1268
02:04:45.360 --> 02:04:47.399
are at their posts.

1269
02:04:48.320 --> 02:04:49.919
Halime is with her sisters.

1270
02:04:51.080 --> 02:04:52.559
Fatma went to the oba.

1271
02:04:52.600 --> 02:04:55.519
She came. everyone
is well. don't worry.

1272
02:04:55.760 --> 02:04:58.679
Your children. your
beys are united.

1273
02:04:59.320 --> 02:05:02.239
The day you get back on your
feet. they will all be by your side.

1274
02:05:05.640 --> 02:05:07.719
My Suleyman...

1275
02:05:07.720 --> 02:05:10.319
my Kasim...

1276
02:05:10.320 --> 02:05:14.119
my dearest ones...

1277
02:05:15.840 --> 02:05:16.879
They...

1278
02:05:16.880 --> 02:05:17.999
Your grandchildren
are also well.

1279
02:05:19.120 --> 02:05:20.079
They pray for your recovery.

1280
02:05:26.600 --> 02:05:27.399
Father!

1281
02:05:31.520 --> 02:05:32.319
Alaeddin!

1282
02:05:32.840 --> 02:05:34.039
Call Alaeddin here!

1283
02:05:38.280 --> 02:05:39.119
Osman.

1284
02:05:42.800 --> 02:05:44.399
If you're playing games...

1285
02:05:44.400 --> 02:05:46.439
No. no! I saw it
with my own eyes.

1286
02:05:46.760 --> 02:05:47.319
I swear.

1287
02:05:48.280 --> 02:05:49.679
Temur Tas had the cure made.

1288
02:05:50.400 --> 02:05:51.919
To use Osman Bey...

1289
02:05:51.920 --> 02:05:52.559
to use him.

1290
02:05:52.600 --> 02:05:54.239
To threaten him.

1291
02:05:54.760 --> 02:05:55.919
Temur Tas will kill me.

1292
02:05:56.840 --> 02:05:57.439
Save me.

1293
02:05:59.160 --> 02:06:00.439
Save me from Temur Tas.

1294
02:06:03.200 --> 02:06:03.919
I beg you.

1295
02:06:15.840 --> 02:06:17.039
Thank goodness. my Bey.

1296
02:06:17.600 --> 02:06:18.959
Hopefully. it will
cure our Osman Bey.

1297
02:06:20.000 --> 02:06:20.919
Come on. let's hurry.

1298
02:06:21.320 --> 02:06:22.719
Let's deliver the
cure to my father.

1299
02:06:32.480 --> 02:06:34.639
No cure I know
will work. mother.

1300
02:06:36.400 --> 02:06:38.119
My father's condition
will not change.

1301
02:06:38.920 --> 02:06:40.799
You are very
tired too. Alaeddin.

1302
02:06:41.360 --> 02:06:42.359
You haven't slept for two days.

1303
02:06:43.400 --> 02:06:45.239
During the day you're on duty.
at night by your father's side.

1304
02:06:46.200 --> 02:06:48.439
How will it be. mother. with my father
in this state and the enemy at the gates?

1305
02:06:49.840 --> 02:06:51.799
How can I sleep
alone with all this?

1306
02:06:53.840 --> 02:06:55.359
Oh. brother. oh!

1307
02:06:55.680 --> 02:06:58.359
Wherever you are.
come out. for God's sake.

1308
02:06:59.160 --> 02:07:00.399
The thing I need most...

1309
02:07:00.440 --> 02:07:02.319
your father's lying time.
where do you go like this?

1310
02:07:07.760 --> 02:07:08.399
Brother!

1311
02:07:09.800 --> 02:07:10.439
Boran!

1312
02:07:10.840 --> 02:07:12.119
Where are you. brother?

1313
02:07:13.040 --> 02:07:14.479
And what's with your clothes?

1314
02:07:15.120 --> 02:07:16.879
The earth splits. the sky
thunders in the middle of the tribe.

1315
02:07:17.360 --> 02:07:19.079
Fatma gets ambushed.
Yigit comes back wounded.

1316
02:07:19.360 --> 02:07:20.639
Where do you go.
leaving them behind?

1317
02:07:22.200 --> 02:07:24.079
I swore not to come
back without this.

1318
02:07:24.800 --> 02:07:25.639
What is this?

1319
02:07:27.560 --> 02:07:28.679
It's my father's cure. mother.

1320
02:07:31.320 --> 02:07:32.679
Do you call yourself
a merchant. brother?

1321
02:07:37.680 --> 02:07:40.239
Come on. my healer brother.
what are you waiting for?

1322
02:07:40.960 --> 02:07:43.039
Do what you do
best. heal my father.

1323
02:07:43.560 --> 02:07:44.319
Thank you. brother.

1324
02:07:45.040 --> 02:07:47.839
But where did you find this?

1325
02:07:49.400 --> 02:07:51.319
I ripped it from the
heart of the enemy.

1326
02:07:52.400 --> 02:07:53.519
Which enemy is this. brother?

1327
02:07:54.320 --> 02:07:56.039
How can I trust a cure
given by the enemy?

1328
02:07:56.720 --> 02:07:59.079
You will trust me. not
the enemy. Aladdin.

1329
02:08:00.440 --> 02:08:01.599
Aren't you the
head of the state?

1330
02:08:02.720 --> 02:08:04.679
If anything happens.
you'll hold me accountable.

1331
02:08:05.480 --> 02:08:06.359
No. I won't.

1332
02:08:06.360 --> 02:08:08.919
If there's a price to pay.
we'll pay it together. brother.

1333
02:08:10.280 --> 02:08:11.479
Alright then.

1334
02:08:11.960 --> 02:08:13.199
Thanks be to Allah.

1335
02:08:19.880 --> 02:08:20.279
In the name of Allah. Most
Gracious. Most Merciful.

1336
02:08:21.200 --> 02:08:24.279
O Healer. O Healer.

1337
02:08:24.560 --> 02:08:28.199
Brother. Nurhan says. We brought
the cure for my blessed father."

1338
02:08:28.880 --> 02:08:29.639
Thank goodness.

1339
02:08:31.160 --> 02:08:32.319
Thank goodness.

1340
02:08:57.880 --> 02:08:59.759
How hard it is
to wait like this.

1341
02:09:00.920 --> 02:09:03.039
When it's my brother Aladdin
I'm waiting for. my heart is at ease.

1342
02:09:03.040 --> 02:09:05.199
Who else is there in this world?

1343
02:09:06.360 --> 02:09:08.159
He cured half of Mith
in one day. brother.

1344
02:09:08.520 --> 02:09:12.279
Good. Sahingsah Bey and Dider
Hatun must be a little relieved.

1345
02:09:13.600 --> 02:09:16.119
Don't ask. they turned
the father upside down.

1346
02:09:16.720 --> 02:09:18.479
They would. it's their child.

1347
02:09:19.800 --> 02:09:22.719
What if something happened to
Kasim and Suleyman. right Lunifer?

1348
02:09:23.640 --> 02:09:25.719
Indeed. may Allah protect them.

1349
02:09:27.040 --> 02:09:30.679
But Sahingah Bey and Dider Hatun
are still angry with you. Orhan Bey.

1350
02:09:30.680 --> 02:09:31.879
Why?

1351
02:09:32.920 --> 02:09:34.679
For saving her sons' lives?

1352
02:09:36.640 --> 02:09:38.599
No matter what I do.
I can't please them.

1353
02:09:46.400 --> 02:09:47.119
My lady...

1354
02:09:48.040 --> 02:09:49.439
Don't worry. he'll be fine.

1355
02:09:50.720 --> 02:09:52.039
It's time for family. Orhan.

1356
02:09:52.800 --> 02:09:54.239
No word from Alaeddin either.

1357
02:10:06.080 --> 02:10:07.719
Thank goodness
he opened his eyes.

1358
02:10:08.080 --> 02:10:08.839
Thank goodness.

1359
02:10:09.880 --> 02:10:10.999
You were the first person
he asked for. mother.

1360
02:10:12.800 --> 02:10:13.759
Come. come.

1361
02:10:16.240 --> 02:10:18.519
I won't wait for my father to
ask for us one by one. brother.

1362
02:10:18.600 --> 02:10:19.479
I won't be able to
stand it. brother.

1363
02:10:20.680 --> 02:10:21.679
Thank goodness.

1364
02:10:34.200 --> 02:10:36.879
Do you want anything. father?
Shall I put a pillow behind your back?

1365
02:10:36.880 --> 02:10:38.719
No. my daughter. no.
I don't want anything.

1366
02:10:38.960 --> 02:10:40.559
Father. shall I rub
your feet? Are you well?

1367
02:10:41.320 --> 02:10:42.119
No. no.

1368
02:10:42.440 --> 02:10:43.519
Osman. you're fine. aren't you?

1369
02:10:43.680 --> 02:10:47.519
I am fine. I am fine.
I will be even better.

1370
02:10:48.400 --> 02:10:51.359
Come on. set a table.

1371
02:10:52.560 --> 02:10:54.159
Let's eat.

1372
02:10:56.000 --> 02:10:57.599
I will cook the meals.

1373
02:10:58.240 --> 02:11:00.279
Just tell me what you
want on the table. father.

1374
02:11:00.640 --> 02:11:04.439
Do you know what I'd
like to see on the table?

1375
02:11:09.720 --> 02:11:11.759
Unity. togetherness.

1376
02:11:13.120 --> 02:11:18.479
May you all be side by side.
shoulder to shoulder at that table.

1377
02:11:19.080 --> 02:11:19.839
As you command. my lord.

1378
02:11:21.760 --> 02:11:25.959
My Osman. the people have gathered
at the head of the tent. they won't leave.

1379
02:11:26.400 --> 02:11:27.839
They await news from you.

1380
02:11:29.160 --> 02:11:32.159
Hayattin. give the good news.

1381
02:11:33.160 --> 02:11:34.639
Let the whole tribe celebrate.

1382
02:11:35.480 --> 02:11:36.439
The command is my lord's.

1383
02:11:44.360 --> 02:11:45.359
Alright. come on.

1384
02:11:51.560 --> 02:11:55.039
Brother. you stormed and
raged at the feast. brother.

1385
02:11:55.040 --> 02:11:58.719
You said "my eyes are on
you'. it really bothered me.

1386
02:12:00.400 --> 02:12:03.999
Brother. how much longer will
you defy my father's command?

1387
02:12:05.440 --> 02:12:07.039
Where will this lead?

1388
02:12:08.680 --> 02:12:13.359
To Bursa. Iznik. 1zmit.

1389
02:12:14.920 --> 02:12:18.319
Wherever my father
dreams of. everywhere.

1390
02:12:18.760 --> 02:12:20.239
Hopefully. brother. hopefully.

1391
02:12:20.840 --> 02:12:22.919
But look. just stop. for
God's sake. just stop.

1392
02:12:23.920 --> 02:12:28.399
You said this is the cure. I didn't make
you repeat your words. I listened to you.

1393
02:12:28.760 --> 02:12:31.599
But while the seal is with
me. you will listen to me too.

1394
02:12:32.400 --> 02:12:35.119
You will not object to my decisions. you will
not put me in a difficult position. brother.

1395
02:12:36.800 --> 02:12:40.599
Come on. the people are waiting.
don't keep them waiting. Come on.

1396
02:12:50.000 --> 02:12:53.159
Brother. you will speak.

1397
02:12:54.920 --> 02:12:58.799
No. the seal is yours. the
command is yours. you speak.

1398
02:12:59.640 --> 02:13:01.959
You are right. the
command is mine.

1399
02:13:03.400 --> 02:13:06.319
Then this is my command
to you. Orhan Bey.

1400
02:13:07.120 --> 02:13:08.559
You will go out and speak.

1401
02:13:10.440 --> 02:13:13.399
Come on. brother. just this once.
listen to your brother. come on.

1402
02:13:14.840 --> 02:13:17.199
Come on. I say. come
on. come on. come on.

1403
02:13:35.840 --> 02:13:41.919
Oh people. I bring you the
greetings of our Osman Bey.

1404
02:13:41.920 --> 02:13:43.319
Praise be to Allah.

1405
02:13:44.920 --> 02:13:50.279
Our Osman Bey is well. on his feet. at
the head of our tribe. praise be to Allah.

1406
02:13:50.800 --> 02:13:56.119
Praise be to Allah. Long live my
Osman Bey. long live my Osman Bey.

1407
02:13:59.640 --> 02:14:03.479
As for Orhan Bey. he saved the lives of our
brothers who fell into an ambush yesterday.

1408
02:14:03.480 --> 02:14:04.319
He saved their lives.

1409
02:14:04.920 --> 02:14:11.439
And he found and brought our father's cure.
saving our Osman Bey's life. May he live long.

1410
02:14:11.440 --> 02:14:15.239
Long live my Orhan Bey.
long live my Orhan Bey.

1411
02:14:18.880 --> 02:14:23.399
My brothers. my
brave ones. my sisters.

1412
02:14:24.960 --> 02:14:27.959
In these lands that our ancestor
Ertugrul made our homeland.

1413
02:14:29.320 --> 02:14:31.439
on the path opened
by my father Osman...

1414
02:14:32.120 --> 02:14:34.959
we have walked together for so
many years. chasing his dream.

1415
02:14:34.960 --> 02:14:42.159
He is the one who saw the dream. and he is the one who
showed the way. Sometimes. he stops you on that path.

1416
02:14:43.400 --> 02:14:47.839
If Osman Bey stopped
me. he must have a reason.

1417
02:14:48.600 --> 02:14:52.919
If he took me off a duty. his
aim is for me to realize the other.

1418
02:14:53.640 --> 02:14:58.039
He is our Bey. If he says fall.
we fall. if he says rise. we rise.

1419
02:14:59.760 --> 02:15:03.079
But we never stray from
his dream for a moment.

1420
02:15:05.280 --> 02:15:11.839
On this road to Constantinople.
first Bursa. on the road to Kaaba. first

1421
02:15:11.840 --> 02:15:13.719
Without crushing
the llkhanids...

1422
02:15:13.720 --> 02:15:17.199
neither you nor we shall stop.

1423
02:15:17.800 --> 02:15:24.839
Long live my Orhan Bey.
long live my Orhan Bey.

1424
02:15:41.840 --> 02:15:46.439
Mother made me a captive in that tribe with
your longing. It's good you came. sister.

1425
02:15:48.680 --> 02:15:49.359
Halime.

1426
02:15:52.080 --> 02:15:54.559
No one else was happy
about my arrival anyway.

1427
02:15:57.040 --> 02:16:00.719
Just look at the faces of my
brothers and sisters-in-law.

1428
02:16:05.960 --> 02:16:09.879
Shame on you. Fatma. every time
you comexthere's an incident in the tribe.

1429
02:16:09.880 --> 02:16:11.079
What should we do?

1430
02:16:11.720 --> 02:16:12.799
Where's a single person?

1431
02:16:13.240 --> 02:16:13.679
Yeah. right.

1432
02:16:14.960 --> 02:16:18.599
I don't want a welcome.
but what about my brothers?

1433
02:16:23.400 --> 02:16:24.959
They're jealous
of you. that's why.

1434
02:16:27.000 --> 02:16:30.919
Why do you say that. girl? Didn't I save
you? What more can your brother do?

1435
02:16:33.680 --> 02:16:41.279
No. I don't know Alaaddin Bey. Look. he
doesn't even smile. He must be jealous.

1436
02:16:42.120 --> 02:16:48.239
Good heavens. When did you notice
me. brother? You were in the mountains.

1437
02:16:48.320 --> 02:16:49.479
I was here in trouble.

1438
02:16:50.400 --> 02:16:55.119
I in the mountains. you in trouble. But
with the same intention. Right. brother?

1439
02:16:55.800 --> 02:16:56.359
Look at that.

1440
02:16:58.960 --> 02:17:04.119
You speak like poetry. Orhan
Bey. Did you have such a talent.

1441
02:17:05.040 --> 02:17:06.799
or were you hiding it from us?

1442
02:17:10.200 --> 02:17:10.959
Huh. sister-in-law?

1443
02:17:12.200 --> 02:17:14.039
Of course. Right. Orhan Bey?

1444
02:17:18.440 --> 02:17:26.319
Ah. ah. Your brother used to read too. Either
Goncagul. or Diken. Right. Alaaddin Bey?

1445
02:17:31.800 --> 02:17:37.639
Yes. brother. You tried to
trap me. now you're in for it.

1446
02:17:38.640 --> 02:17:40.159
It was a bit like that. brother.

1447
02:17:41.200 --> 02:17:41.679
It was.

1448
02:17:42.440 --> 02:17:42.799
Cheers.

1449
02:17:53.880 --> 02:17:55.039
Come on in.

1450
02:17:56.840 --> 02:17:57.959
My Bey. come in.

1451
02:17:59.040 --> 02:18:01.279
I told you not to get up
immediately. but you wouldn't listen.

1452
02:18:01.280 --> 02:18:02.479
Come. come. Walk-and sit.

1453
02:18:02.560 --> 02:18:08.599
Calm down. calm down. I
earned a bowl of soup. didn't I?

1454
02:18:09.880 --> 02:18:17.439
I defeated the Angel of Death
after all. Thanks to Orhan.

1455
02:18:20.440 --> 02:18:21.199
Here you go.

1456
02:18:26.320 --> 02:18:27.079
In the name of Allah. the Most
Gracious. the Most Merciful.

1457
02:18:28.160 --> 02:18:35.399
My Bey. you say thanks to Orhan. but Alaaddin
slowed it down with his remedy. I brought the cure.

1458
02:18:38.240 --> 02:18:43.879
As I said. tomorrow you'll be much better after
going to the hot springs. inshallah. father.

1459
02:18:44.320 --> 02:18:45.479
I will. by God's grace.

1460
02:18:46.280 --> 02:18:46.759
Inshallah.

1461
02:18:48.360 --> 02:18:56.919
Oh. your smiles. aren't they something?
After all this time. they came like medicine.

1462
02:18:58.960 --> 02:19:06.359
My Bey. listening from that door. I understood
that my strength comes from here. From this table.

1463
02:19:07.560 --> 02:19:08.359
from you all.

1464
02:19:09.560 --> 02:19:17.919
My sons become my cure. My daughters. daughters-in-law.
grandchildren are my reason for living.

1465
02:19:18.520 --> 02:19:22.159
and my companions
share my destiny.

1466
02:19:23.240 --> 02:19:24.559
May you live long. my Bey.

1467
02:19:24.560 --> 02:19:27.039
Always. my Bey.
your path is our path.

1468
02:19:30.560 --> 02:19:32.639
Come on. enjoy your meal.

1469
02:19:39.120 --> 02:19:40.159
Thank you. my Bey.

1470
02:19:53.360 --> 02:19:58.239
Grandpa. did you really see the
Angel of Death? Did you defeat him?

1471
02:20:06.920 --> 02:20:13.119
Not yet. Kasim. not
yet. Let's take Bursa first.

1472
02:20:14.240 --> 02:20:17.439
then we'll settle accounts
with the Angel of Death.

1473
02:20:17.440 --> 02:20:20.079
If you let my father. he
will take it. grandfather.

1474
02:20:25.320 --> 02:20:36.919
Your father was your age. From that time on. he
made my dream his dream. He worked very hard.

1475
02:20:38.600 --> 02:20:48.199
He became one of the greatest commanders Kayi has ever
seen. But you will work even harder than your father.

1476
02:20:49.000 --> 02:20:56.999
You will gallop non-stop to spread the
divine word of Allah to the whole world.

1477
02:20:59.720 --> 02:21:04.599
May my Lord make our blessed
dream of a state come true.

1478
02:21:04.840 --> 02:21:05.399
Amen.

1479
02:21:09.880 --> 02:21:10.519
Boran.

1480
02:21:11.080 --> 02:21:11.399
My Bey.

1481
02:21:13.080 --> 02:21:14.719
Strike the strings
of that kopuz.

1482
02:21:15.680 --> 02:21:16.519
The command is mine.

1483
02:21:19.080 --> 02:21:20.479
Come on.

1484
02:22:13.160 --> 02:22:26.519
May Allah be with the Turks. The roads
became my 'friend' Tongues spoke to me.

1485
02:22:27.520 --> 02:22:40.719
May the Turan lands exist. May the enemies
be destroyed. May Allah be with the Turks.

1486
02:22:42.920 --> 02:22:50.319
May the Turan lands exist. "
May Allah be with the Turks.

1486
